%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rising%20Food%20Prices%20Push%20November%20Retail%20Inflation%20to%207.37%25%20for%20Farm%20Workers%2C%207%25%20for%20Rural%20Labourers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F01175204%2Fagriculture.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20November%2C%20retail%20inflation%20for%20farm%20workers%20increased%20to%207.37%25%2C%20and%20for%20rural%20labourers%2C%20it%20rose%20to%207.13%25%2C%20primarily%20driven%20by%20higher%20prices%20of%20specific%20food%20items%2C%20according%20to%20an%20official%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20figures%20were%20higher%20than%20October%E2%80%99s%20rates%20of%207.08%25%20and%206.92%25%20for%20farm%20workers%20and%20rural%20labourers%2C%20respectively%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2FEconomy%2Fretail-inflation-for-farm-workers-rises-to-737-in-november-713-for-rural-labourers%2Farticle67661380.ece%3Futm_source%3Deveningwrap%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_campaign%3DNewsletter%26pnespid%3D6_ZpUXlGK65F0KLE.mqzHpzUvxipD4J2N_anxegy9BhmieMsRj8EZti71eIxgHy1O0uR3NCG%5C%22%3EPTI%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFood%20inflation%20stood%20at%209.38%25%20and%209.14%25%20for%20agricultural%20and%20rural%20workers%2C%20respectively%2C%20in%20November%20compared%20to%20the%20respective%20figures%20of%208.42%25%20and%208.18%25%20in%20October%202023%2C%20and%206.19%25%20and%206.05%25%20recorded%20in%20the%20corresponding%20month%20of%20previous%20year%20(November%202022)%2C%20PTI%20cited%20the%20labour%20ministry%20statement%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20comparable%20numbers%20were%206.87%25%20and%206.99%25%20in%20November%20last%20year%2C%20the%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20indices%20have%20been%20analysed%3A%20CPI-AL%20(Consumer%20Price%20Index-Agricultural%20Labourers)%20and%20CPI-RL%20(rural%20labourers).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECPI-AL%20measures%20the%20changes%20over%20time%20in%20the%20prices%20paid%20by%20agricultural%20laborers%20for%20a%20specified%20basket%20of%20goods%20and%20services.%20Similarly%2C%20CPI-RL%20measures%20the%20changes%20over%20time%20in%20the%20prices%20paid%20by%20rural%20labourers%20for%20a%20basket%20of%20goods%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPI-AL%20in%20November%20this%20year%20increased%2012%20points%20to%201%2C253%2C%20while%20the%20index%20for%20rural%20workers%20advanced%2011%20points%20to%201%2C262%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20indices%20were%201%2C241%20points%20and%201%2C251%20points%2C%20respectively%2C%20in%20October%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20was%20driven%20by%20an%20increase%20in%20prices%20of%20rice%2C%20wheat%20atta%2C%20pulses%2C%20onion%2C%20turmeric%20whole%2C%20garlic%2C%20mixed%20spices%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20noted%20that%20there%20has%20been%20an%20upward%20trend%20in%20the%20index%20across%20all%20the%20states%20except%20West%20Bengal%20(both%20CPI-AL%20and%20CPI-RL%20indices%20decreased)%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20(CPI-AL%20index%20decreased).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703253254000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F01175204%2Fagriculture.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Frising-food-prices-push-november-retail-inflation-to-7-37-for-farm-workers-7-for-rural-labourers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20figures%20were%20higher%20than%20October's%20rates%20of%207.08%25%20and%206.92%25%20for%20farm%20workers%20and%20rural%20labourers%2C%20respectively.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google's%20culture%20shock%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoffs-pivots-race-for-ai-supremacy-inside-google-tumultuous-2023-2023-