%20Games%20gold%20medallist%20Anita%20Sheoran%2C%20who%20was%20backed%20by%20the%20protesting%20wrestlers.%20Mr%20Singh%20got%2040%20votes%20against%20only%207%20for%20Ms%20Sheoran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20emotional%20letter%20to%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Mr%20Punia%20pointed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrij-bhushans-dabdaba-remark-after-aide-wins-wrestling-federation-poll-4716552%5C%22%3EBrij%20Bhushan's%20remark%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20election%20results%20on%20Thursday%2C%20when%20he%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Edabdaba%20tha%2C%20dabdaba%20rahega%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(our%20dominance%20will%20continue).%20The%20Olympian%20said%20it%20was%20this%20mental%20pressure%20that%20forced%20Ms%20Mallikh%20to%20quit%20the%20sport%20and%20that%20the%20wrestlers%20involved%20in%20the%20protest%20spent%20the%20whole%20night%20crying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20understand%20where%20to%20go%2C%20what%20to%20do%20and%20how%20to%20live.%20The%20government%20and%20the%20people%20gave%20me%20so%20much%20respect.%20Should%20I%20continue%20to%20suffocate%20under%20the%20burden%20of%20this%20respect%3F%20In%20the%20year%202019%2C%20I%20was%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Shri.%20I%20was%20also%20honoured%20with%20the%20Khel%20Ratna%20and%20Arjuna%20Award.%20I%20was%20very%20happy%20when%20I%20received%20these%20honours.%20It%20seemed%20that%20life%20had%20been%20successful.%20But%2C%20today%2C%20I%20am%20much%20unhappier%20than%20I%20was%20happy%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20these%20honours%20are%20suffocating%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Punia%20wrote%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20only%20one%20reason%20for%20this%3A%20It%20was%20wrestling%20that%20got%20me%20these%20honours%20and%20female%20wrestlers%20are%20now%20having%20to%20quit%20that%20very%20sport%20for%20their%20safety%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Women%20Making%20India%20Proud'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wrestler%20said%20sport%20has%20made%20a%20huge%20difference%20to%20the%20lives%20of%20girls%20and%20that%20no%20one%20could%20have%20imagined%20boys%20and%20girls%20playing%20together%20in%20the%20villages.%20He%20said%20women%20are%20making%20India%20proud%20in%20sports%20arenas%20on%20the%20international%20stage%20and%20asserted%20that%20this%20had%20only%20been%20possible%20because%20of%20the%20courage%20of%20the%20first%20generation%20of%20sportswomen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20even%20the%20shadow%20of%20those%20who%20have%20dominated%20or%20will%20continue%20to%20dominate%20scares%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20and%20now%20they%20have%20completely%20taken%20over%20again.%20The%20photo%20of%20them%20with%20garlands%20around%20their%20necks%20must%20have%20reached%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Punia%20said%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20daughters%20who%20were%20to%20become%20the%20brand%20ambassadors%20of%20'Beti%20Bachao%20Beti%20Padhao'%20were%20put%20in%20such%20a%20situation%20that%20they%20had%20to%20step%20back%20from%20their%20sport.%20We%20'respectable'%20wrestlers%20could%20not%20do%20anything.%20I%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20live%20my%20life%20as%20'respectable'%20after%20female%20wrestlers%20were%20insulted.%20Such%20a%20life%20would%20be%20suffocating.%20That's%20why%20I%20am%20returning%20this%20'honour'%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703252280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F4idfg1fg_bajrang-punia-650_625x300_22_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrestler-bajrang-punia-says-he-is-returning-his-padma-shri-to-pm-modi-amid-wrestling-body-row-4722726%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bajrang%20Punia%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20he%20has%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20will%20be%20returning%20his%20Padma%20Shri.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%