uot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFisher%20said%20other%20travelers%20have%20been%20instrumental%20in%20helping%20with%20their%20travel%20plans%2C%20while%20Crowley%20said%20the%20information%20they%20exchanged%20was%20usually%20more%20up-to-date%20and%20accurate%20than%20what%20was%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBe%20respectful%20toward%20local%20communities.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Small%20bowls%20of%20meats%2C%20soup%20and%20condiments%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658166a4a79e5746976ad053%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20said%20trying%20out%20local%20cuisines%20is%20important.%3Cp%3EZach%20%26amp%3B%20Haley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECrowley%20said%20a%20daily%20iced%20coffee%20is%20a%20home%20comfort%20that%20she%20can't%20live%20without%2C%20though%20she's%20still%20on%20the%20hunt%20to%20find%20one%20up%20to%20her%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20food%20and%20beverage%20options%20the%20couple%20has%20tried%20on%20their%20travels%20have%20been%20less%20familiar%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Fisher%20and%20Crowley%20were%20traveling%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Ftravel%2Farticle%2F20190102-pamir-highway-a-wild-ride-across-central-asia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPamir%20Highway%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20said%20they%20stayed%20at%20a%20guesthouse%20where%20food%20was%20prepared%20by%20a%20family.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20obviously%20not%20a%20grocery%20store%20nearby%2C%20so%20you%20just%20eat%20whatever%20they%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Crowley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20one%20of%20the%20most%20interesting%20things%20they%20sampled%20was%20while%20spending%20the%20night%20in%20a%20yurt%20with%20a%20family%20in%20Mongolia%2C%20where%20they%20were%20given%20a%20drink%20called%20mountain%20water.%20A%20local%20guide%20had%20warned%20them%20that%20it%20would%20be%20rude%20according%20to%20local%20culture%20not%20to%20eat%20what%20was%20prepared%20by%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20it's%20water%20mixed%20with%20vodka%2C%20mixed%20with%20sheep%20fat.%20It%20looked%20like%20water%20in%20a%20glass%20with%20a%20few%20drops%20of%20oil%20floating%20on%20the%20surface%2C%26quot%3B%20Crowley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFisher%20said%20though%20he%20is%20an%20adventurous%20eater%2C%20this%20was%20a%20difficult%20delicacy%20to%20savor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20'If%20I%20just%20finish%20it%2C%20then%20I'm%20good.'%20So%20I%20just%20got%20it%20down.%20And%20they're%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20you%20liked%20it%3F'%20And%20they%20poured%20me%20another%20glass%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20couple%20might%20not%20be%20likely%20to%20crave%20every%20local%20delicacy%2C%20they%20said%20it's%20important%20to%20try%20things%2C%20and%20that%20it%20can%20be%20much%20cheaper%20to%20eat%20locally%20than%20scouting%20for%20a%20home%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20makes%20for%20really%20cool%20and%20interesting%20experiences%2C%26quot%3B%20Crowley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETravel%20like%20a%20local.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20girl%20on%20a%20motorbike%20with%20hills%20and%20a%20shack%20in%20the%20back%20(left)%2C%20a%20man%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20bike%20on%20a%20cliff%20(right).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65816704a79e5746976ad05c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThough%20traveling%20can%20be%20uncomfortable%2C%20it%20makes%20for%20good%20memories.%3Cp%3EZach%20%26amp%3B%20Haley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFisher%20said%20walking%20is%20an%20underrated%20mode%20of%20transportation%20that's%20vital%20in%20understanding%20what%20locals%20get%20up%20to%20when%20traveling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quo