uot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20housing%20market%20is%20beginning%20to%20ease%2C%20but%20%26quot%3BShark%20Tank%26quot%3B%20star%20Barbara%20Corcoran%20maintains%20that%20waiting%20for%20a%20better%20deal%20would%20be%20a%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20her%20stance%20even%20before%20mortgage%20rates%20sank%2C%20and%20as%20they%20have%20tumbled%20from%20October's%20high%20of%208%25%2C%20she%20warned%20a%20big%20price%20swing%20may%20be%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20some%20advice%20from%20the%20real%20estate%20expert%20about%20buying%20a%20home%20as%20the%20housing%20market%20reaches%20an%20inflection%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENow%20is%20the%20time%20to%20buy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20rates%20tumble%2C%20housing%20is%20becoming%20more%20affordable%2C%20but%20Corcoran%20said%20buyers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-outlook-us-mortgage-rates-fall-prices-barbara-corcoran-2023-12%5C%22%3Eshouldn't%20try%20to%20wait%20out%20the%20market.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20good%20time%20to%20buy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FGMA%2FLiving%2Fvideo%2Fbarbara-corcoran-answers-real-estate-questions-105576050%5C%22%3EABC%20News%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month.%20%26quot%3BThings%20aren't%20going%20to%20get%20any%20better%20for%20homebuyers.%20If%20interest%20rates%20continue%20to%20come%20down%20%E2%80%94%20as%20they%20will%20and%20as%20everyone's%20expecting%20it%20%E2%80%94%20prices%20will%20go%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20logic%20behind%20that%20goes%20like%20this%3A%20The%20minute%20a%20reasonable%20rate%20threshold%20is%20reached%20for%20enough%20people%2C%20demand%20for%20homes%20will%20surge.%20And%20as%20demand%20surges%2C%20so%20will%20the%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20world's%20going%20to%20be%20out%20there%20competing%20with%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BYou'll%20be%20paying%20more%20for%20your%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFind%20a%20great%20broker%20and%20get%20pre-qualified%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20homeowners%20may%20want%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20sweetest%20deal%20they%20can%20get%2C%20but%20Corcoran%20added%20that%20her%20mantra%20holds%20true%20even%20for%20first-time%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFind%20yourself%20a%20great%20broker%20who%20knows%20how%20to%20hustle%2C%20because%20there's%20always%20a%20deal%20to%20be%20had%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20the%20ABC%20News%20interview.%20%26quot%3BNo%20exceptions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20new%20homebuyers%20should%20also%20get%20pre-qualified%20for%20their%20home%20loans%2C%20giving%20them%20a%20readily%20available%20source%20of%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20on%20equal%20footing%20with%20everybody%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuy%20a%20second%20home%2C%20if%20you%20can%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorcoran%20was%20also%20asked%20if%20it's%20smarter%20to%20sell%20an%20existing%20home%20to%20buy%20a%20new%20one%2C%20or%20if%20it's%20better%20to%20buy%20a%20second%20home%20and%20rent%20out%20the%20first%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20buyers%20who%20have%20paid%20off%20their%20mortgages%2C%20she%20recommended%20holding%20onto%20that%20existing%20house%20and%20renting%20it%20out%2C%20while%20buying%20a%20second%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20becomes%20a%20cash%20machine%20going%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20get%20an%20investment%20property%20that%20the%20tenant's%20paying%20for%20and%20you%20go%20out%20and%20buy%20a%20new%20home%20by%20putting%20a%20second%20mortgage%20on%20your%20house.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERates%20aren't%20that%20high%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20could%20drop%20to%206%25%2C%20Corcoran%20said.%20But%20regardless%20of%20the%20drop%2C%20current%20rates%20are%20not%20