Ch2%3EThe%20missing%20song%20in%20'The%20Muppet%20Christmas%20Carol'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E(Spoilers%20for%20this%20holiday%20classic%20if%20you%20haven't%20seen%20it)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20scene%20happens%20when%20Scrooge%20(played%20to%20perfection%20by%20Michael%20Caine)%20travels%20to%20his%20younger%20days%20with%20the%20Ghost%20of%20Christmas%20Past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScrooge%20sees%20the%20moment%20his%20fianc%C3%A9e%20Belle%20(played%20by%20Meredith%20Braun)%20breaks%20off%20their%20relationship.%20But%20the%20scene%20ends%20abruptly%20when%20Past%20Scrooge%20tells%20her%20he%20still%20loves%20her%2C%20and%20she%20responds%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20did%20once.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECut%20to%20sobbing%20Muppets%20and%20a%20crying%20Michael%20Caine%20as%20she%20quietly%20walks%20away.%20Wait%2C%20what%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20movie's%20final%20scene%2C%20Scrooge%20sings%20a%20short%20song%20called%20%26quot%3BThe%20Love%20We%20Found%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20ditty%20that%20comes%20out%20of%20nowhere%20at%20the%20emotional%20climax%20of%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20gives%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20Director%20Brian%20Henson's%20original%20cut%20of%20the%20movie%20featured%20an%20extended%20scene%20where%20Braun%20sings%20%26quot%3BThe%20Love%20is%20Gone%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20tear-jerking%20ballad%20about%20how%20their%20relationship%20has%20crumbled%20and%20she's%20leaving%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20song%20ends%20as%20a%20duet%20where%20Caine%20%E2%80%94%20tears%20in%20his%20eyes%20and%20his%20voice%20breaking%20%E2%80%94%20sings%20the%20final%20verse%20with%20her%20as%20she%20exits.%20It's%20a%20tragic%20moment%20that%20makes%20Scrooge's%20cruelty%20much%20more%20sympathetic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20you%20probably%20guessed%20right%3A%20the%20final%20song%20of%20the%20movie%20is%20a%20version%20of%20the%20missing%20song%20with%20different%20lyrics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20puts%20Scrooge's%20redemption%20in%20a%20more%20satisfying%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20full%20version%20of%20the%20movie%2C%20Scrooge%20%E2%80%94%20who%20had%20shunned%20kindness%20after%20his%20past%20heartbreak%20%E2%80%94%20now%20sings%20the%20same%20notes%20his%20fianc%C3%A9e%20once%20did%2C%20but%20this%20time%20embraces%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20love%3A%20caring%20for%20his%20fellow%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20great!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20was%20'The%20Love%20is%20Gone'%20cut%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20agreed%20the%20song%20was%20a%20good%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHenson%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Few.com%2Fmovies%2Fthe-muppet-christmas-carol-when-love-is-gone%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Entertainment%20Weekly%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Disney%20studio%20boss%20Jeffrey%20Katzenberg%20suggested%20the%20song%20get%20cut%20because%20kids%20were%20getting%20%26quot%3Bantsy%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20seats%20during%20test%20screenings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHenson%2C%20reluctantly%2C%20took%20it%20out.%20But%20he%20and%20songwriter%20Paul%20Williams%20(who%20co-wrote%20the%20famed%20%26quot%3BRainbow%20Connection%26quot%3B)%20were%20proud%20of%20the%20song.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20things%20I've%20ever%20written%20in%20my%20life%2C%20that%20song%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20told%20Entertainment%20Weekly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20Caine%20praised%20the%20%26quot%3Bvery%20beautiful%20song%26quot%3B%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP8SPHMk-lAE%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20behind-the-scenes%20clip%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20VHS%20release%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Muppet%20Christmas%20Carol%26quot%3B%20put%20the%20song%20back%20in%2C%20but%20subsequent%20releases%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20song%20out%20since%20Disney%20lost%20the%20original%20film%20negative%2C%20and%20splicing%20in%20the%20VHS%20recording%20looked%20too%20obvious%20because%20of%20the%20sudden%20drop%20in%20film%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20the%20song%20w