yan%20Ellison%20and%20Sophie%20Darsy%20were%20living%20in%20Stockholm%20when%20they%20decided%20to%20buy%20a%20sailboat.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20couple%20set%20off%20in%202016%20with%20the%20plan%20to%20sail%20for%20a%20year%20while%20working%20remotely.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEight%20years%20later%2C%20they%20are%20still%20sailing.%20The%20couple%20shared%20how%20they%20juggle%20work%20and%20travel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Ryan%20Ellison%20and%20Sophie%20Darsy%20about%20living%20and%20working%20full-time%20on%20a%20sailboat.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERyan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%202016%2C%20I%2C%20Ryan%20Ellison%2C%20sent%20a%20WhatsApp%20message%20to%20my%20girlfriend%2C%20Sophie%20Darsy%2C%20about%20a%20couple%20who%20sold%20all%20their%20belongings%20to%20cruise%20the%20world%20on%20a%20sailboat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImagine%20my%20surprise%20when%20Sophie%20said%20she'd%20be%20willing%20to%20do%20it%20for%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20we've%20built%20a%20life%20we%20love%20and%20found%20success%20in%20fulfilling%20and%20important%20careers%20%E2%80%94%20all%20while%20living%20on%20the%20boat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20medical%20emergencies%2C%20weathered%20bad%20storms%2C%20and%20struggled%20both%20on%20a%20relationship%20level%20and%20with%20our%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'd%20both%20bought%20apartments%20in%20Stockholm%20during%20the%20crazy%20housing-market%20days%2C%20so%20we%20were%20able%20to%20take%20some%20equity%20out%20of%20those%20apartments%20to%20buy%20our%2040-foot%20boat%2C%20the%20Polar%20Seal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223050%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20on%20the%20bow%20of%20a%20sail%20boat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65842c51a79e5746976c1607%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221716%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20bought%20'Polar%20Seal%2C'%20a%20Beneteau%20Oceanis%2040%20from%202007.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sophie%20Darsy%20and%20Ryan%20Ellison%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESophie%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Before%20we%20embarked%2C%20Ryan%20had%20just%20taken%20on%20investors%20in%20a%20battery-tech%20startup%20he'd%20founded%20in%202015%20with%20his%20college%20roommates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERyan%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESophie%20was%20recovering%20from%20corporate%20burnout%20and%20had%20just%20begun%20her%20journey%20as%20a%20creative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20thought%20we'd%20try%20sailing%20for%20a%20year%20in%202016%20and%20return%20to%20Sweden.%20Eight%20years%20later%2C%20our%20apartments%20are%20rented%20long-term%2C%20and%20we're%20still%20adventuring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20organize%20sailing%20around%20our%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221524%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20sailing%20a%20sailboat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65842d4bcefc010bea261296%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221018%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEllison%20steering%20the%20sailboat%20at%20sea.%3Cp%3ESophie%20Darsy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERyan%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFor%20every%20week%20we%20sail%2C%20we%20are%20on%20anchor%20or%20in%20port%20for%20five%20or%20six%20weeks.%20Regardless%20of%20being%20at%20sea%20or%20in%20port%2C%20we%20still%20work%20like%20everyone%20else%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20few%20adjustments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20to%20work%20whenever%20we%20can%2C%20sometimes%20even%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20Sophie%20advises%20companies%20in%20Europe%20and%20I%20work%20with%20the%20US.%20We%20often%20have%20different%20office%20hours%20from%20each%20other%20and%20our%20coworkers%2C%20especially%20if%20we're%20in%20a%20more%20remote%20part%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20us%20might%20need%20to%20be%20on%20a%20call%20while%20we're%20sailing%2C%20and%20while%20technology%20such%20as%20Starlink%20has%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20stay%20connected%2C%20it%20isn't%20fail-proof.%20We%20plan%20our%20travel%20and%20leisure%20around%20our%20work%20schedules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22755%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sailboat%20interior%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65842e03cefc010bea261311%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22520%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20both%20work%20from%20the%20sailboat's%20cabin.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sophie%20Darsy%20and%20Ryan%20Ellison%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ESailing%20changed%20our%20career%20paths%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESophie%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20Ryan%20took%20the%20risk%20of%20living%20on%20a%20boat%20while%20scaling%20his%20startup%2C%20he%20left%20his%20job%20at%20another%20startup%20in%20Sweden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdakotalithium.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDakota%20Lithium%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20only%20been%20around%20for%20a%20year%20when%20we%20set%20sail.%20Ryan%20worked%20remotely%20with%20his%20team%20to%20continue%20scaling%20%E2%80%94%20all%20while%20at%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20boat%20was%20the%20first%20to%20have%20Dakota%20Lithium%20batteries%20installed.%20Because%20of%20our%20positive%20experience%2C%20other%20boaters%20have%20also%20put%20Dakota%20Lithium%20batteries%20in%20their%20vessels.%20Now%20the%20company%20is%20a%20major%20battery%20brand%20in%20sailing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221752%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sailboat%20at%20sunset.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65842d97cefc010bea2612f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22984%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDarsy%20documents%20the%20couple's%20travels%20as%20a%20content%20creator.%3Cp%3ESophie%20Darsy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERyan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sophie%20began%20documenting%20our%20adventures%20and%20cracking%20jokes%20on%20camera%20with%20a%20DSLR%2C%20a%20great%20camera%2C%20given%20to%20her%20by%20a%20friend.%20What%20started%20out%20as%20a%20hobby%20turned%20into%20a%20professional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ryanandsophie.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%2C%20Sophie%20makes%20a%20living%20from%20filming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESophie%20wanted%20flexibility%20in%20her%20work%2C%20so%20she%20also%20began%20consulting%20with%20companies%20to%20create%20e-learning%20content%20%E2%80%94%20an%20extension%20of%20her%20video-editing%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20both%20of%20us%2C%20sailing%20allowed%20us%20the%20freedom%20to%20reinvent%20our%20careers%20as%20well%20as%20our%20personal%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20manage%20our%20alone%20time%20differently%20than%20most%20couples%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221352%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20couple%20jumping%20off%20a%20sailboat%20into%20the%20ocean.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658437f4cefc010bea2616ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221004%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDarsy%20and%20Ellison%20jumping%20off%20the%20Polar%20Seal.%3Cp%3ESophie%20Darsy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESophie%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20the%20boat%2C%20we%20share%20a%20tiny%20space%2024%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20seven%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20work%20side%20by%20side%20in%20the%20cabin%20all%20day.%20Ryan's%20work%20requires%20him%20to%20be%20on%20the%20phone%20a%20lot%2C%20whereas%20my%20work%20requires%20me%20to%20focus%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoing%20both%20at%20the%20same%20time%20is%20really%20difficult%20to%20do%20in%20such%20a%20small%20area%2C%20so%20we%20have%20to%20communicate%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20work%2C%20we%20sail%20together%20and%20spend%20evenings%20exploring%20ports%20or%20the%20open%20sea.%20Having%20our%20relationship%20in%20a%20healthy%20place%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20making%20this%20life%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20learned%20that%20while%20other%20couples%20have%20breaks%20in%20their%20relationships%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20we%20take%20ours%20in%20large%20chunks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221510%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20couple%20stood%20on%20the%20deck%20of%20a%20sailboat%20in%20front%20of%20a%20sunset.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658438d4a79e5746976c1a6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221004%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20stands%20on%20the%20deck%20of%20Polar%20Seal%20at%20sunset.%3Cp%3ESophie%20Darsy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERyan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20Sophie%20approached%20me%20saying%20she%20wanted%20to%20go%20home%20to%20France%20for%20some%20alone%20time%2C%20I%20felt%20threatened.%20However%2C%20we%20realized%20that%20we%20needed%20time%20apart%20to%20keep%20life%20on%20the%20boat%20enjoyable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20great%20couples'%20therapist%20helping%20us%20navigate%20this%20unique%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20our%20dog%20Barnacle%20has%20also%20helped%20because%20it%20encourages%20us%20to%20get%20off%20of%20the%20boat%20to%20take%20her%20for%20walks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20on%20a%20boat%20with%20a%20dog.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65843a1f1c5c7b8c9a0ae307%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223127%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESophie%20Darsy%20with%20their%20dog%20Barnacle.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sophie%20Darsy%20and%20Ryan%20Ellison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20have%20the%20opportunity%2C%20one%20of%20us%20will%20get%20a%20desk%20at%20a%20coworking%20space%20or%20take%20time%20to%20go%20to%20the%20gym%20%E2%80%94%20all%20ways%20to%20keep%20this%20lifestyle%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20reward%20of%20living%20on%20the%20sailboat%20is%20extremely%20high%2C%20but%20so%20is%20the%20cost%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERyan%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELiving%20on%20a%20boat%20for%20six%20years%20is%20a%20dream%20for%20some%20people.%20The%20truth%20is%20that%20we%20hold%20each%20other's%20lives%20in%20our%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sophie%20got%20a%20third-degree%20burn%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Africa%2C%20I%20had%20to%20act%20as%20her%20medic%20until%20we%20sailed%20to%20Spain%20for%20professional%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20on%20a%20sailboat%20means%20working%20together%20and%20trusting%20each%20other%20as%20crewmates%20as%20well%20as%20partners%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20require%20excellent%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sailboat%20from%20above%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658439101c5c7b8c9a0ae2f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221002%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Polar%20Seal%20from%20above.%3Cp%3ESophie%20Darsy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20it%20costs%20to%20sail%20full-time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESophie%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20cost%20of%20living%20on%20the%20boat%20can%20also%20vary%20drastically%2C%20depending%20on%20what%20part%20of%20the%20world%20you%20are%20in%20and%20what%20you%20are%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Ryan%20always%20says%2C%20you%20can%20live%20on%20a%20boat%20on%20whatever%20budget%20you%20have%20%E2%80%94%20from%20almost%20nothing%20to%20living%20like%20a%20king.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Northern%20Europe%2C%20we%20could%20get%20by%20on%20%241%2C500%20a%20month.%20But%20in%20Bermuda%2C%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20from%20anchoring%20and%20marina%20fees%20to%20insurance%20to%20food%20%E2%80%94%20is%20significantly%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221786%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Polar%20Seal%20sailing%20into%20a%20port.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65843970cefc010bea2616fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22980%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Polar%20Seal%20sailing%20into%20port.%3Cp%3ESophie%20Darsy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20take%20breaks%20from%20sailing%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20family%20and%20friends%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERyan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sometimes%2C%20we%20need%20to%20take%20a%20vacation%20from%20it%20all%2C%20so%20we%20leave%20the%20boat%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20out%20of%20the%20year%20and%20go%20to%20land.%20This%20lets%20us%20spend%20more%20quality%20time%20with%20our%20families%20in%20France%20and%20Iowa.%20If%20we%20don't%20stay%20with%20family%2C%20we%20stay%20with%20friends%20or%20rent%20an%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWherever%20we%20are%2C%20we%20still%20work.%20But%20on%20land%2C%20daily%20amenities%20like%20a%20flushing%20toilet%2C%20a%20dishwasher%2C%20and%20unlimited%20showers%20make%20life%20more%20convenient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20at%20sea%2C%20we%20miss%20having%20a%20supportive%20community%20around%20us.%20We've%20had%20to%20learn%20to%20make%20friends%20fast%20and%20say%20goodbye%20fast%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20hard.%20We've%20had%20to%20cultivate%20a%20strong%20relationship%20because%20we%20are%20everything%20to%20each%20other%20on%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20pointing%20to%20the%20horizon%20on%20a%20sailboat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658439b61c5c7b8c9a0ae302%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22968%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20more%20practical%20boat%20is%20on%20the%20couples'%20horizon.%3Cp%3ESophie%20Darsy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20want