2C%20with%20billions%20in%20Ukraine%20aid%20blocked%20by%20Republicans%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20plans%20are%20being%20formed%20to%20announce%20the%20move%20on%20the%20second%20anniversary%20of%20Russia's%20invasion%20in%20February%2C%20and%20US%20officials%20are%20in%20discussions%20with%20allies%20including%20France%20and%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20plan%20has%20its%20pitfalls%2C%20critics%20say%2C%20and%20there%20are%20concerns%20the%20move%20could%20undermine%20the%20global%20financial%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20powerful%20concern%20is%20that%20doing%20so%20could%20harm%20international%20financial%20stability%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20dollar%20and%20euro's%20status%20as%20reserve%20currencies%20%E2%80%94%20by%20undermining%20the%20essential%20trust%20involved%20in%20depositing%20reserves%20with%20other%20nations%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2Fm2wAN%23selection-2269.185-2269.411%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20the%20board%20of%20The%20Financial%20Times%20in%20an%20editorial.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%20say%20that%20countries%20could%20hesitate%20to%20keep%20funds%20in%20dollars%20if%20they%20believe%20they%20could%20be%20seized%2C%20accelerating%20plans%20by%20some%20nations%20to%20move%20away%20from%20the%20currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgathe%20Demarais%2C%20a%20fellow%20on%20geoeconomics%20at%20the%20European%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%2C%20wrote%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2023%2F11%2F27%2Frussia-ukraine-war-central-bank-reserves-assets-seize-reparations-sanctions%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520key%2520argument%2520for%2520those%2Cknown%2520as%2520de%252Ddollarization).%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Foreign%20Policy%20in%20November%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20move%20could%20have%20unforeseen%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Western%20democracies%20have%20previously%20set%20a%20precedent%20by%20seizing%20Russia's%20assets%2C%20how%20will%20these%20states%20manage%20to%20convince%20anyone%20that%20China%20or%20India%20have%20no%20right%20to%20confiscate%20Western%20holdings%20if%20they%20so%20wish%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20also%20been%20debates%20about%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20move%2C%20with%20the%20assets%20protected%20under%20sovereign%20immunity%20rules%2C%20though%20some%20legal%20experts%20argue%20that%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20was%20so%20grave%20a%20breach%20of%20international%20law%20that%20it%20has%20forfeited%20the%20right%20to%20legal%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20funds%20are%20held%20in%20European%20banks%2C%20and%20a%20final%20decision%20has%20reportedly%20not%20yet%20been%20made%20on%20whether%20to%20go%20through%20with%20the%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20has%20contacted%20the%20White%20House%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-eyes-using-300-russia-frozen-assets-help-ukraine-backfire-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703246857000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65857112a79e5746976c9429%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-eyes-using-300-russia-frozen-assets-help-ukraine-backfire-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20move%20comes%20amid%20signs%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20in%20some%20Western%20countries%20may%20be%20waning%2C%20with%20billions%20in%20Ukraine%20aid%20blocked%20by%20Republicans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Porter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-eyes-using-300-russia-frozen-assets-help-ukraine-backfire-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It%20May%20Be%20a%20Mistake%20to%20Dismiss%20China%20as%20Copy-Paste%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F09085822%2F24939411081_39dd945cb2_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20governor%20Raghuram%20Rajan%20recently%20made%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fidea-exchange%2Fraghuram-rajan-at-idea-exchange-to-turn-back-on-democracy-when-ideas-are-the-future-currency-is-just-the-most-blind-thing-to-do-9072152%2F%5C%22%3Eclaim%20about%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20can%20be%20challenged%20on%20facts.%20He%20says%20China%20has%20leadership%20in%20manufacturing%20but%20not%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20ideas%20and%20innovation%20where%20the%20US%20dominates%2C%20essentially%20because%20of%20its%20open%20and%20democratic%20character.%20His%20assertion%20is%20that%20non-democratic%20systems%20do%20not%20lead%20in%20innovation%2Fideas.%20Overall%2C%20it%20may%20be%20true%20that%20the%20US%20has%20dominated%20the%20innovation%20landscape%20for%20much%20of%20the%20past%20half%20a%20century.%20But%20it%20is%20equally%20true%20that%20China%20has%20hugely%20caught%20up%20in%20cutting%20edge%20innovation%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20we%20are%20fundamentally%20opposed%20to%20the%20Chinese%20political%20system%2C%20which%20many%20of%20us%20are%2C%20one%20can%20still%20objectively%20see%20China%E2%80%99s%20big%20strides%20in%20the%20innovation%2Fideas%20space%20which%20has%20led%20to%20it%20closing%20the%20gap%20with%20the%20US%20and%20even%20forge%20ahead%20in%20some%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESometime%20ago%2C%20%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20the%20findings%20of%20an%20independent%20think%20tank%2C%20Australian%20Strategic%20Policy%20Institute%20(ASPI)%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fchina-leads-us-global-competition-key-emerging-technology-study-says-2023-03-02%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20China%20leads%20the%20world%20in%2037%20out%20of%2044%20critical%20technologies%20in%20the%20field%20of%20defence%2C%20space%2C%20robotics%2C%20energy%2C%20environment%2C%20advanced%20materials%2C%20quantum%20technology%20and%20artificial%20intelligence.%20The%20West%20is%20lagging%20behind%20in%20many%20of%20these%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20Rajan%E2%80%99s%20sweeping%20assertion%20that%20China%20cannot%20be%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20ideas%20and%20innovation%20is%20not%20borne%20out%20by%20facts%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20such%20massive%20leaps%20of%20progress%20in%20innovation%20is%20happening%20in%20a%20non-democratic%20society%20is%20a%20subject%20for%20a%20separate%20study.%20There%20is%20enough%20academic%20literature%20to%20suggest%20that%20much%20of%20incremental%C2%A0%20growth%20and%20prosperity%20in%20the%2021st%20century%20are%20being%20produced%20by%20societies%20which%20are%20governed%20by%20either%20authoritarian%20or%20partially%20democratic%20regimes.%20These%20regimes%20have%20evolved%20their%20own%20hybrid%20versions%20of%20State-cum-market-led%20capitalism%20models.%20The%20whole%20notion%20of%20the%2021st%20century%20belonging%20to%20Asia%20seems%20to%20be%20based%20on%20such%20a%20hybrid%20framework%20of%20State-cum-market%20model%20of%20capitalism.%20This%20is%20also%20described%20as%20State%20Capitalism%20by%20many%20political%20scientists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20the%20US%20seems%20to%20be%20aping%20this%20framework%20with%20its%20hugely%20State-led%20model%20of%20a%20new%20industrial%20policy%20to%20counter%20China%20in%20the%20field%20of%20semiconductor%20chips%20and%20green%20energy%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F10%2F17%2Fhow-the-chips-act-is-aiming-to-restore-a-us-lead-in-semiconductors.html%5C%22%3EUS%E2%80%99s%20Chips%20Act%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.energy.gov%2Flpo%2Finflation-reduction-act-2022%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520President%2527s%2520Inflation%2520Reduction%2520Act%2Cenergy%2520manufacturing%252C%2520and%2520putting%2520the%5C%22%3EInflation%20Reduction%20Act%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20together%20aimed%20at%20delivering%20nearly%20%241%20trillion%20of%20subsidies%20for%20semiconductor%20chips%20and%20green%20transition%2C%20are%20a%20tribute%20to%20China%E2%80%99s%20growing%20influence%20in%20these%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20also%20stunned%20the%20world%20recently%20with%20a%20new%2C%20highly%20sophisticated%20semiconductor%20chip%20technology%20for%20electronics%2C%20which%20may%20obviate%20its%20need%20to%20depend%20on%20inputs%20from%20the%20West%20incrementally.%20This%20was%20widely%20reported%20in%20the%20global%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYangtze%20Memory%20Technologies%20Corp%2C%20which%20was%20added%20to%20the%20US%20trade%20blacklist%20last%20December%2C%20made%20a%20%E2%80%9Csurprise%20technology%20leap%E2%80%9D%20through%20a%20solid-state%20drive%20(ZhiTai%20Ti600%201TB)%20launched%20in%20July%20without%20much%20fanfare.%20What%20turns%20that%20from%20surprising%20to%20significant%20is%20the%20fact%20that%203D%20NAND%20memory%20is%20an%20essential%20component%20for%20high-performance%20computing%20(HPC)%2C%20such%20as%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20says%20%3Cem%3ETechwire%20Asia%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20tech%20news%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20it%20may%20not%20be%20easy%20to%20write%20off%20China%20as%20merely%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20old%20economy%20and%20a%20laggard%20in%20innovation%20and%20new%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20person%20who%20read%20the%20writing%20on%20the%20wall%20very%20early%20was%20Henry%20Kissinger%2C%20former%20US%20secretary%20of%20State%2C%20who%20passed%20away%20recently.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20visits%20to%20Delhi%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20Kissinger%20told%20a%20group%20of%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20journalists%20in%20an%20off%20the%20record%20chat%20(I%20was%20present)%20that%20China%20was%20forging%20ahead%20of%20the%20US%20in%20many%20critical%20areas%20of%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghuram%20Rajan%20further%20makes%20the%20argument%20that%20the%20US%20keeps%20reinventing%20itself%20via%20innovation%2C%20starting%20from%20the%20Sputnik%20moment%20when%20the%20Soviets%20launched%20the%20first%20artificial%20satellite%2C%20Sputnik%20I.%20The%20successful%20launch%20came%20as%20a%20shock%20to%20the%20US%20as%20it%20had%20hoped%20to%20be%20the%20first%20to%20accomplish%20this%20scientific%20feat.%20However%2C%20the%20US%20came%20from%20behind%20to%20more%20than%20match%20the%20Soviets%20in%20this%20field.%20Later%2C%20in%20the%201980s%20and%201990s%2C%C2%A0%20the%20US%20overcame%20the%20Japanese%20threat%20of%20taking%20leadership%20in%20the%20export%20of%20manufacturing%20sophisticated%20electronics%2C%20automobiles%2C%20etc.%3Cbr%3E%5CnNow%2C%20the%20US%20is%20dealing%20with%20the%20Chinese%20threat%20via%20innovation%20in%20green%20transition%20and%20semiconductor%20chips%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20closer%20scrutiny%20suggests%20that%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20US%20overcame%20these%20threats%20partly%20through%20coercion%20and%20deploying%20its%20geopolitical%20muscle.%20Remember%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investopedia.com%2Farticles%2Fforex%2F09%2Fplaza-accord.asp%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Plaza%2520Accord%2520was%2520an%2Cthe%2520country%2527s%2520%2522lost%2520decade.%2522%5C%22%3EPlaza%20Accord%20of%201985%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20forced%20Japan%20to%20make%20its%20own%20currency%20more%20expensive%2C%20thereby%20hitting%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20exports%20in%20the%20late%201980s.%20It%20led%20to%20what%20many%20perceived%20as%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20lost%20decade%20in%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20question%20is%20whether%20the%20US%20has%20the%20same%20geo-political%20dominance%20and%20hegemony%20today%20to%20do%20to%20China%20what%20it%20did%20to%20Japan%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20or%20even%20more%20importantly%2C%20what%20it%20did%20to%20the%20Soviets%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%20the%2020th%20century%3F%20What%20is%20clear%20is%20that%20the%20game%20of%20thrones%20in%20critical%2C%20cutting%20edge%20technologies%20have%20acquired%20totally%20new%20dynamics%20in%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20in%20which%20the%20growing%20middle%20powers%20are%20asserting%20themselves%20like%20never%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20India%20has%20to%20be%20very%20careful%20about%20how%20it%20aligns%20itself%20in%20the%20collaborative%20technology%20framework%C2%A0%20globally.%20It%20may%20be%20a%20mistake%20for%20India%20to%20become%20part%20of%20the%20proposed%20US-India%20critical%20tech%20corridor%20to%20the%20exclusion%20of%20possible%20collaborations%20elsewhere.%20It%20will%20go%20against%20its%20overall%20%E2%80%9Cmulti-alignment%E2%80%9D%20foreign%20policy%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreenfdc.org%2Fgreen-public-transport-innovation-in-china-an-opportunity-for-bri-countries%2F%5C%22%3Egreen%20transition%20for%20transportation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20China%20is%20way%20ahead%20of%20the%20US%20as%20it%20controls%2080%25%20of%20the%20global%20supply%20chain.%20India%E2%80%99s%20auto%20sector%20which%20has%20developed%20a%20solid%20manufacturing%20supply%20chain%20ecosystem%20over%20the%20last%20three%20decades%20can%20easily%20collaborate%20with%20China%20for%20the%20transformation%20of%20its%20electric%20vehicle%20industry.%20It%20can%20collaborate%20with%20the%20US%20on%20other%20cutting%20edge%20technologies.%20Putting%20all%20eggs%20in%20the%20US%20basket%20may%20not%20be%20wise%20given%20the%20way%20multiple%20technology%20regimes%20are%20shaping%20up%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20century%20may%20not%20produce%20the%20same%20patterns%20as%20the%20previous%20one%20in%20terms%20of%20US%E2%80%99s%20dominance%2C%20whatever%20the%20political%20system%20various%20powers%20are%20operating%20in.%20The%20reality%20is%20critical%20technology%20development%20is%20becoming%20more%20delinked%20from%20the%20nature%20of%20political%20systems%2C%20unlike%20what%20Raghuram%20Rajan%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20that%20matter%20even%20the%20famed%20democratic%20political%20systems%20of%20the%20West%2C%20which%20were%20held%20up%20as%20exemplars%20of%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20seem%20to%20be%20in%20somewhat%20uncharted%20territory%20today%20as%20they%20erode%20pluralist%20ethos%20via%20bottom%20up%20democratic%20processes.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20larger%20battle%20for%20the%20values%20of%20freedom%20and%20openness%20will%20continue%20both%20within%20nations%20and%20transnationally.%20But%20such%20battles%20may%20be%20shaped%20somewhat%20differently%20with%20some%20key%20influences%20deriving%20from%20the%20new%2021st%20century%20alignments%20of%20geopolitics%20and%20geoeconomics.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703246404000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F09085822%2F24939411081_39dd945cb2_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fit-may-be-a-mistake-to-dismiss-china-as-copy-paste%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Must%20wake%20up%20and%20smell%20the%20coffee%20on%20what%20is%20going%20on%20in%20the%20middle%20kingdom%20after%20the%20chip%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fit-may-be-a-mistake-to-dismiss-china-as-copy-paste%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20'The%20Exorcist'%20turns%2050%2C%20star%20Linda%20Blair%20says%20it's%20not%20actually%20a%20horror%20movie%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Linda%20Blair%20American%20actress%20and%20activist%20on%20a%20blue%20background%20with%20scenes%20from%20The%20Exorcist%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6571e50658e7c0c29a2a9b81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAlbert%20L.%20Ortega%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20ABA%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELinda%20Blair%20is%20best%20known%20for%20playing%20demonically%20possessed%20Regan%20MacNeil%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Exorcist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20actor%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20to%20celebrate%20the%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20William%20Friedkin's%20movie.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBlair%20says%20%26quot%3BThe%20Exorcist%26quot%3B%20isn't%20a%20horror%20movie%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20religious%20thriller.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20day%20after%20Christmas%20in%201973.%20Usually%20this%20time%20of%20year%2C%20movie%20theaters%20were%20packed%20with%20families%20wanting%20to%20watch%20something%20cheery%20over%20the%20holidays.%20But%20something%20peculiar%20happened%20this%20particular%20year.%20The%20big%20festive%20theatrical%20release%20wasn't%20a%20movie%20fit%20for%20all%20the%20family%20%E2%80%94%20though%2C%20indeed%2C%20there%20was%20a%20family%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20there%20were%20reports%20of%20people%20vomiting%2C%20fainting%2C%20and%20even%20several%20heart%20attacks%2C%20according%20to%20a%20piece%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1974%2F01%2F27%2Farchives%2Fthey-wait-hoursto-be-shocked-the-exorcist-got-mixed-reviews-why-has.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20following%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fthe-exorcist-movie-surprising-facts-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Exorcist%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20director%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwilliam-friedkin-dead-director-obituary-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWilliam%20Friedkin%3C%2Fa%3E's%20now-classic%20tale%20of%20a%20desperate%20single%20mother%20whose%2012-year-old%20daughter%20is%20demonically%20possessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20the%20mention%20of%20the%20film%20is%20likely%20to%20conjure%20images%20of%20young%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmost-iconic-horror-movie-villains-of-all-time-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERegan%20MacNeil%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20played%20by%20a%20then-14-year-old%20Linda%20Blair%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8QjrBjdb2T8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprojectile-vomiting%20pea%20soup%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20crab-walking%20down%20the%20stairs%2C%20or%20her%20head%20swiveling%20360%20degrees%20with%20a%20sickening%20crunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFifty%20years%20later%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Exorcist%26quot%3B%20still%20sets%20the%20benchmark%20for%20the%20horror%20genre%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20the%20first%20to%20be%20nominated%20for%20best%20picture%20at%20the%20Oscars%2C%20and%20won%20best%20adapted%20screenplay%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20in%20large%20part%20due%20to%20how%20Blair's%20performance%20as%20the%20preteen%20protagonist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAkIqFK3KoZ4%3Ffeature%3Dshared%26t%3D105%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Econtinues%20to%20unsettle%20audiences%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Few%20movies%20have%20been%20audacious%20enough%20to%20feature%20a%2012-year-old%20girl%20stabbing%20herself%20in%20the%20crotch%20with%20a%20crucifix%2C%20and%20rightly%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey'd%20never%20seen%20anything%20like%20that%2C%20and%20I%20was%20so%20young.%20People%20weren't%20sure%20what%20to%20make%20of%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Blair%20tells%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BBilly%20Friedkin%20tested%20me%20with%20makeup%2C%20psychology%2C%20and%20many%20different%20things%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20I%20was%20okay%20to%20do%20the%20film.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Linda%20Blair%20as%20Reagan%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Exorcist.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651ffe4c9f7ca8b2bbdb8d04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22562%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELinda%20Blair%20as%20Reagan%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Exorcist.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bros.%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20days%20Blair%20spent%20on%20set%2C%20inhabiting%20Regan's%20unsettled%20mind%2C%20were%20long.%20%26quot%3BIt%20probably%20took%20us%20three%20to%20five%20days%20to%20do%20one%20scene%2C%20where%20today%20you%20have%20to%20finish%20it%20in%20half%20a%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20movie%20was%20eventually%20released%2C%20the%20heavy%20religious%20themes%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Exorcist%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1177%2F09526951211004465%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esparked%20debate%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20whether%20it%20was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20sacrilegious.%20Fifty%20years%20on%2C%20Blair%20says%20that%20it%20isn't%20the%20horror%20film%20that%20everyone%20says%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20proud%20to%20be%20part%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20something%20that%20I%20know%20has%20rocked%20the%20world%20in%20many%20different%20ways.%20I've%20explained%20it's%20a%20theological%20thriller.%20It's%20not%20a%20horror%20film.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBill%20Blatty%20intended%20for%20it%20to%20shock%20the%20world%2C%20to%20kind%20of%20wake%20them%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20referring%20to%20author%20William%20Peter%20Blatty%2C%20whose%201971%20novel%20of%20the%20same%20name%20serves%20as%20the%20movie's%20source%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Linda%20Blair%20as%20Reagan%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Exorcist%20II%3A%20Heretic.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651ffeb46e038039826b683c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELinda%20Blair%20as%20Regan%20in%20%26quot%3BExorcist%20II%3A%20The%20Heretic.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bros.%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBlair's%20portrayal%20of%20Regan%20shocked%20the%20world%2C%20but%20adding%20to%20the%20hysteria%20around%20the%20movie%20was%20the%20press%20attention%20the%20actor%20had%20to%20cope%20with%20upon%20its%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20had%20conferences%20where%20a%20hundred%20or%20more%20people%20from%20the%20press%20would%20show%20up.%20And%20it%20was%20quite%20something%20to%20look%20out%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Blair%20remembers.%20%26quot%3BA%20sea%20of%20reporters%20asking%20about%20religion%20and%20all%20the%20aspects%20of%20the%20movie.%20And%20I'm%20trying%20to%20answer%20them.%20I'm%2015%20years%20old%20going%2C%20'Well%2C%20I%20%3Cem%3Ethink%3C%2Fem%3E%20so%E2%80%A6'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20surrounding%20the%20movie%20only%20served%20to%20amplify%20it%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Exorcist%26quot%3B%20grossed%20%24193%20million%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20was%20the%20highest-grossing%20movie%20released%20in%201973.%20A%20sequel%20was%20all%20but%20guaranteed.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlair%20reprised%20her%20role%20as%20Regan%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fthe-exorcist-movies-ranked-by-critics-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1977's%20%26quot%3BExorcist%20II%3A%20The%20Heretic%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20the%20film%20failed%20to%20impress%20both%20critics%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20a%20lowly%2011%25%20critics'%20score%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rottentomatoes.com%2Fm%2Fexorcist_ii_the_heretic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERotten%20Tomatoes%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20fans%20of%20the%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Blair%2C%20the%20only%20redeeming%20quality%20about%20the%20movie%20was%20getting%20to%20work%20with%20the%20legendary%20Richard%20Burton%2C%20who%20played%20priest%20Father%20Lamont.%20Burton%2C%20a%20veritable%20Hollywood%20heartthrob%20whose%20relationship%20with%20Elizabeth%20Taylor%20was%20the%20stuff%20of%20legend%20by%20then%2C%20made%20quite%20the%20impression%20on%20young%20Blair%2C%20who%20was%20by%20then%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20one%20side%20of%20your%20mind%2C%20you're%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20my%20God%2C%20it's%20Richard%20Burton!'%26quot%3B%20she%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20other%20side%20is%20just%20holding%20it%3A%20'Just%20keep%20going.%20Stay%20in%20the%20moment.%20You're%20an%20actor%2C%20enjoy%20the%20ride.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20%26quot%3BExorcist%20II%2C%26quot%3B%20Blair%20has%20had%20a%20patchwork%20of%20Hollywood%20credits%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BRoller%20Boogie%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BHell%20Night%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20late%201970s%20and%20'80s%2C%20and%201990's%20%26quot%3BExorcist%26quot%3B%20spoof%2C%20%26quot%3BRepossessed.%26quot%3B%20But%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20her%20passion%20lies%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlair%20stepped%20away%20from%20the%20film%20industry%20in%20the%201990s%20to%20dedicate%20her%20time%20to%20rescuing%20dogs%2C%20largely%2C%20she%20says%2C%20because%20she%20felt%20like%20she%20needed%20a%20greater%20purpose%20than%20just%20making%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20rescuing%20dogs%20out%20of%20shelters%20in%201997%20after%20my%20mother%20had%20passed.%20I%20was%20really%20devastated%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20I%20had%20worked%20for%20everybody%2C%20had%20just%20done%20all%20these%20amazing%20films%2C%20but%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20my%20own%20path.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20founded%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lindablairworldheart.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinda%20Blair%20WorldHeart%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202003%2C%20and%20has%20since%20helped%20rescue%20and%20rehome%20thousands%20of%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20go%20back%20to%20regular%20life%20as%20I%20knew%20it%20until%20changes%20are%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20Blair%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20wants%20more%20legal%20support%20for%20animal%20shelters%20across%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnyone%20that's%20in%20animal%20welfare%20will%20tell%20you%20it's%20like%20PTSD.%20It's%20so%20shocking%20what%20we're%20witnessing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continues.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20full-blown%20crisis%20that%20has%20to%20stop.%20How%20we%20treat%20our%20animals%20is%20how%20we%20treat%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Linda%20Blair%20and%20a%20dog%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658462be1c5c7b8c9a0b0f51%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELinda%20Blair%20arrives%20at%20the%202018%20American%20Rescue%20Dog%20Show%20in%20Beverly%20Hills%2C%20California.%3Cp%3EJerod%20Harris%2FWireImage%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20has%20become%20Blair's%20life's%20work%3B%20she%20manages%20all%20the%20day-to-day%20operations%20herself%2C%20and%20has%20200%20dogs%20living%20on%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20because%20of%20her%20important%20work%20that%20Blair%20almost%20didn't%20reprise%20her%20role%20as%20Regan%20in%20the%20recent%20%26quot%3BExorcist%26quot%3B%20reboot%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Exorcist%3A%20Believer.%26quot%3B%20Luckily%2C%20the%20film's%20producers%20managed%20to%20arrange%20a%20small%20window%20for%20Blair%20to%20shoot%20a%20cameo%2C%20which%20sees%20Regan%20reunite%20with%20her%20mother%2C%20Chris%20MacNeil%2C%20played%20by%20Ellen%20Burstyn.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlair%20also%20worked%20closely%20with%20director%20David%20Gordon%20Green%20to%20ensure%20that%20young%20actors%20Olivia%20O'Neill%20and%20Lidya%20Jewett%2C%20who%20play%20the%20franchise's%20latest%20teen%20possession%20victims%2C%20Katherine%20and%20Angela%2C%20were%20given%20sufficient%20support%20on%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20definitely%20took%20the%20girls%20under%20my%20wing%20and%20made%20sure%20they%20were%20taken%20care%20of.%20If%20they%20needed%20a%20psychologist%2C%20if%20they%20needed%20any%20type%20of%20religious%20mentor%2C%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20there%20for%20them%20at%20any%20time%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20knew%20it's%20work%2C%20it's%20a%20film.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20full%20circle%20moment%2C%20says%20Blair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20like%20what%20Billy%20Friedkin%20did%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BMaking%20sure%20I%20was%20fine%20for%20the%20life%20journey%2C%20how%20to%20survive%2C%20because%20life%20is%20difficult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-exorcist-linda-blair-50-years-horror-religious-thriller-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703246401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6571e4e60ec98e92f74d1982%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-exorcist-linda-blair-50-years-horror-religious-thriller-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20Exorcist%26quot%3B%20star%20Linda%20Blair%20speaks%20to%20Business%20Insider%20to%20celebrate%20the%20iconic%20movie's%2050th%20anniversary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ejacobs%40insider.com%20(Eammon%20Jacobs)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-exorcist-linda-blair-50-years-horror-religious-thriller-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20Opens%20Up%20About%20Mis