s.com%2F2023%2F12%2F21%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-gaza-bomb-investigation.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Israel%20has%20both%20the%20GBU-39%20and%20MK-84%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20context%2C%20the%20GBU-39%2C%20which%20is%20far%20more%20precise%20bomb%2C%20and%20can%20strike%20targets%20underground%20-%20a%20key%20requirement%20for%20Tel%20Aviv%20as%20it%20combats%20Hamas'%20infamous%20tunnel%20network.%20It%20has%20an%20explosive%20capacity%20of%2037%20pounds%20and%20on%20detonation%20in%20open%20areas%20can%20kill%2C%20or%20injure%2C%20people%20in%20a%201%2C000-foot%20radius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MK-84%20has%2025%20times%20more%20explosive%20power%20and%20a%20blast%20radius%20thrice%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EA%20Times%20visual%20investigation%20found%20that%20Israel%20routinely%20dropped%202%2C000-pound%20bombs%20in%20areas%20it%20designated%20safe%20for%20civilians%20in%20Gaza.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FgtydRJw5N7%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FgtydRJw5N7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20(%40nytimes)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnytimes%2Fstatus%2F1738074599978365063%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20greater%20fragmentation%20danger%20from%20the%20larger%20bomb%3B%20this%20is%20when%20pieces%20of%20the%20metal%20casing%20explode%20on%20impact%20and%20can%20shoot%20hundreds%20of%20feet%20all%20around%2C%20killing%20people%20the%20bomb%20didn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF%2C%20US%20officials%20told%20the%20Times%2C%20prefers%20the%20larger%20bombs%20because%20they%20are%20more%20effective%20at%20destroying%20tunnels%2C%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbiggest-hamas-tunnel-with-4-km-long-network-found-under-gaza-says-israel-4692191%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBiggest%20Hamas%20Tunnel%26quot%3B%20With%204-Km%20Network%20Found%20Under%20Gaza%3A%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20when%20these%20bombs%20explode%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20devastation%2C%20they%20leave%20%26quot%3Bearthquake-like%26quot%3B%20craters%20than%20can%20measure%20over%2020%20metres%20wide%20and%20more%20than%2013%20metres%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20most%20worryingly%2C%20American%20intelligence%20sources%20believe%20over%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20nearly%2030%2C000%20air-to-surface%20bombs%20dropped%20on%20Gaza%20so%20far%20are%20%26quot%3Bdumb%20bombs%26quot%3B%2C%20meaning%20they%20are%20not%20guided%20and%20pose%20greater%20civilian%20threats%2C%20particularly%20in%20densely-populated%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MK-84%20is%20a%20non-guided%20bomb%20that%20is%20designed%20for%20%26quot%3Bmaximum%20blast%20and%20explosive%20effects%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Did%20Israel%20Say%20To%20These%20Reports%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20use%20of%20these%20bombs%20in%20civilian%20areas%2C%20an%20Israeli%20military%20spokesperson%20told%20the%20Times%20the%20%26quot%3Bpriority%26quot%3B%20is%20%26quot%3Bdestroying%20Hamas%26quot%3B%20and%20dismissed%20%26quot%3Bquestions%20of%20this%20kind%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20will%20be%20looked%20into%20%26quot%3Blater%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%2C%20which%20has%20said%20it%20is%20making%20every%20effort%20to%20minimise%20civilian%20deaths%2C%20is%20constrained%20in%20its%20efforts%20to%20root%20out%20Hamas%20terrorists%20by%20the%20urban%20landscape%20in%20Gaza%2C%20where%20buildings%20are%20packed%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-begi