0that%20the%20IDF%20killed%20three%20of%20the%20people%20it%20was%20claiming%20to%20be%20rescuing%2C%20after%20they%20had%20stripped%20their%20shirt%2C%20scrawled%20SOS%20in%20Hebrew%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisrael-hamas-war-killed-hostages-were-holding-white-flag%2Flive-67742012%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewere%20waving%20a%20white%20flag%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20IDF%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20distinguish%20between%20combatants%20and%20non-combatants%20is%20in%20doubt.%20Moreover%2C%20with%20about%20three%20IDF%20personnel%20being%20killed%20daily%20during%20military%20operations%20seems%20to%20indicate%20that%20neither%20the%20will%20to%20fight%2C%20nor%20the%20ability%2C%20of%20Hamas%20has%20been%20severely%20degraded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20stated%20goals%20%E2%80%93%20the%20liberation%20of%20those%20captured%2C%20most%20of%20them%20civilians%20and%20many%20of%20them%20elderly%20or%20children%2C%20and%20the%20elimination%20of%20a%20militant%20group%20that%20wilfully%20murdered%20hundreds%20of%20civilians%20%E2%80%93%20were%20legitimate.%20But%20the%20way%20that%20Israel%20has%20prosecuted%20this%20war%20indicates%20either%20the%20IDF%20is%20entirely%20incompetent%2C%20or%20other%20unstated%20goals%20are%20taking%20precedence.%20Since%20October%207%2C%20the%20world%20has%20seen%20Israel%20killing%20thousands%20of%20civilians%20and%20taking%20hundreds%20more%20civilian%20captives.%20Israel%20may%20justify%20these%20actions%20as%20%E2%80%98retaliatory%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20the%20end%20result%20is%20a%20(much%20larger)%20replica%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20atrocities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20release%20of%20110%20civilians%20by%20Hamas%20in%20the%20first%20round%20of%20ceasefire%20negotiations%2C%20initially%20resisted%20by%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20cabinet%2C%20showed%20that%20there%20were%20other%20ways%20to%20do%20things.%20Since%20Israel%20released%20240%20Palestinian%20women%20and%20children%20as%20part%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20though%2C%20it%20showed%20the%20world%20that%20Hamas%20was%20hardly%20the%20only%20actor%20kidnapping%20and%20detaining%20civilians.%20Israel%20tries%20Palestinians%20under%20a%20military%20court%2C%20which%20has%20a%20conviction%20rate%20of%2096-99%25%20for%20any%20act%20of%20resisting%20its%20military%20occupation.%20It%20also%20holds%20hundreds%20as%20detainees%20even%20without%20conviction%2C%20often%20for%20years.%20The%20release%20of%20Palestinian%20women%20and%20children%20led%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2023%2F12%2F21%2F1217758546%2Fhamas-support-palestinians-west-bank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esurge%20of%20support%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20Hamas%20in%20both%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20the%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scale%20and%20manner%20of%20Israeli%20military%20operations%20are%20such%20that%20even%20its%20committed%20allies%20%E2%80%93%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20most%20European%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20are%20starting%20to%20use%20words%20like%20%E2%80%9Cindiscriminate%20bombing%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Ckilling%20rage%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20slowly%20starting%20to%20assert%20that%20the%20killing%20has%20to%20stop%2C%20or%20at%20least%2C%20be%20contained.%20Even%20Germany%2C%20which%20has%20defined%20the%20defence%20of%20Israel%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Staatsr%C3%A4son%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20or%20national%20interest%20%E2%80%93%20due%20to%20the%20crimes%20of%20the%20Nazis%2C%20has%20now%20started%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcease-fire-in-gaza-why-germany-abstained-in-un-votes%2Fa-67772509%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eabstain%20from%20UN%20votes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20rather%20than%20merely%20following%20Israeli%20points.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENone%20of%20this%20has%20impacted%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20strategies.%20Partially%2C%20this%20is%20because%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lowyinstitute.org%2Fpublications%2Fisrael-war-about-more-recovering-hostages-destroying-hamas-it-could-last-long-time%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etwo%20of%20the%20unstated%20goals%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20IDF%20campaign%20are%20to%20restore%20the%20deterrence%20capability%20of%20Israel%2C%20and%20to%20re-establish%20trust%20between%20the%20state%20and%20society%20that%20such%20a%20massive%20security%20failure%20will%20not%20happen%20again.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20military%20campaign%20is%20as%20much%20a%20psychological%20operation%20%E2%80%93%20directed%20both%20at%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20enemies%20and%20its%20own%20population%20to%20recreate%20an%20aura%20of%20invincibility%20that%20the%20Hamas%20October%207%20attacks%20tore%20apart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20meshes%20well%20with%20the%20political%20aims%20of%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20and%20his%20extreme%20right%20cabinet.%20Netanyahu%20has%20always%20been%20a%20believer%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9CIron%20Wall%E2%80%9D%20concept%20enunciated%20by%20the%20Russian-born%20Ze%E2%80%99ev%20Jabotinsky.%20In%20his%20famous%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fen.jabotinsky.org%2Fmedia%2F9747%2Fthe-iron-wall.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E1923%20essay%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20same%20name%2C%20Jabotinsky%20stated%20that%20the%20Palestinians%20would%20not%20abandon%20resisting%20the%20colonisation%20of%20their%20land%20by%20Zionists%20until%20all%20hope%20of%20resistance%20was%20defeated%20by%20an%20iron%20wall%20of%20force.%20The%20survival%20of%20any%20form%20of%20resistance%20among%20the%20Palestinians%20is%20anathema%20for%20Netanyahu%2C%20and%20the%20catastrophic%20October%207%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20proved%20that%20he%20was%20deluded%20in%20believing%20he%20had%20bludgeoned%20Palestinians%20into%20total%20submission.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%