%20Supreme%20Court%20Judge%20AK%20Patnaik%20had%20said%20the%20judiciary%20has%20taken%20several%20good%20steps%20since%20he%20retired%20in%202014%20and%20the%20courts%20should%2C%20while%20staying%20within%20their%20limits%2C%20seize%20opportunities%20to%20%26quot%3Bclean%26quot%3B%20legislatures.%20Justice%20Patnaik%20was%20on%20the%20bench%20that%20gave%20the%20landmark%20judgment%20disqualifying%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20from%20the%20date%20of%20conviction%20in%20a%20criminal%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV's%20Ashish%20Kumar%20Bhargava%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20judge%20also%20highlighted%20the%20live-streaming%20of%20cases%20as%20a%20great%20step%20forward%20by%20the%20judiciary%2C%20saying%20it%20brings%20in%20transparency%20and%20keeps%20both%20judges%20and%20lawyers%20in%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisqualification%20Ruling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Patnaik%20was%20part%20of%20the%20two-judge%20bench%2C%20including%20SJ%20Mukhopadhyaya%2C%20which%20struck%20down%20a%20sub-section%20of%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%20that%20allowed%20a%20lawmaker%20convicted%20of%20a%20criminal%20offence%20and%20sentenced%20to%20a%20minimum%20of%20two%20years%20in%20prison%20to%20continue%20in%20office%20while%20his%20or%20her%20appeal%20was%20pending.%20In%20the%202013%20judgment%2C%20which%20was%20based%20on%20a%20petition%20by%20lawyer%20and%20activist%20Lily%20Thomas%2C%20the%20court%20said%20such%20lawmakers%20would%20be%20disqualified%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20ruling%20also%20played%20a%20role%20in%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20disqualification%20as%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20in%20March.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20reasoning%20behind%20the%20judgment%2C%20Justice%20Patnaik%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20Parliament%20is%20sovereign%2C%20it%20has%20got%20very%20vast%20powers%2C%20subject%20to%20the%20Constitution.%20Legislative%20assemblies%20in%20the%20state%20also%20have%20vast%20powers.%20Therefore%2C%20those%20who%20go%20as%20representatives%20to%20these%20bodies%20must%20have%20a%20clean%20reputation%20so%20that%20people%20will%20trust%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20has%20been%20convicted%20and%20gets%20disqualified%20under%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%20he%20should%20not%20remain%20in%20Parliament%20or%20the%20Assembly%20unless%20his%20conviction%20is%20stayed.%20But%20there%20was%20a%20provision%20allowing%20people%20to%20stay%20on%20if%20they%20appeal.%20I%20thought%20this%20is%20not%20correct%2C%20either%20you%20get%20your%20conviction%20stayed%20or%20you%20get%20out%20and%20come%20back%20elected%20if%20your%20conviction%20is%20set%20aside%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20retired%20judge%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Patnaik%20said%20this%20is%20necessary%20to%20keep%20the%20legislative%20bodies%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%2C%20to%20keep%20the%20Houses%20clean%2C%20people's%20representatives%20must%20go%20out%20when%20they%20are%20convicted%20and%20sentenced%20for%20more%20than%20two%20years.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20the%20judiciary%20must%20avail%20this%20kind%20of%20opportunity%20whenever%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20exercise%20power%20within%20the%20judicial%20domain%2C%20without%20crossing%20the%20limits%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%20and%20clean%20up.%20I%20thought%20I%20could%20do%20it%2C%20I%20just%20cut%20down%20that%20provision.%20We%20had%20the%20power%20to%20strike%20down%20that%20provision%20if%20it%20violates%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20Better%2C%20What%20Isn't%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Patnaik%20said%20live-streaming%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20Constitution%20benches%20are%20deciding%20key%20matters%20have%20been%20welcome%20developments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20there%20was%20no%20live-streaming%20of%20cases%2C%20the%20interactions%20between%20judges%20and%20lawyers%20sometimes%20used%20to%20get%20rough.%20Those%20interactions%20are%20now%20gone%20because%20both%20lawyers%20and%20judges%20are%20conscious%20that%20they%20are%20being%20watched%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20good%20development%20is%20that%2C%20in%20my%20time%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Supreme%20Court%20judges%20was%20low%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20matters%20was%20so%20high%20that%20the%20chief%20justice%20could%20not%20constitute%20five-judge%20Constitution%20benches...%20It%20is%20very%20good%20that%20Constitution%20benches%20are%20hearing%20constitutional%20matters%20now%2C%20because%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20basically%20the%20highest%20constitutional%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20development%20that%20the%20retired%20judge%20has%20not%20liked%20is%20long%20judgments%2C%20sometimes%20running%20into%20400%20pages.%20He%20said%20precise%20judgments%20will%20be%20appreciated%20and%20understood%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703244240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F7c41so58_retired-supreme-court-judge-ak-patnaik_625x300_22_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcourts-should-seize-opportunities-to-clean-legislatures-retired-judge-4722652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Supreme%20Court%20Judge%20AK%20Patnaik%20had%20said%20the%20judiciary%20has%20taken%20several%20good%20steps%20since%20he%20retired%20in%202014%20and%20the%20courts%20should%2C%20while%20staying%20within%20their%20limits%2C%20seize%20opportunities%20to%20%26quot%3Bclean%26quot%3B%20legislatures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcourts-should-seize-opportunities-to-clean-legislatures-retired-judge-4722652%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv