%20will%20come%20roaring%20back%2C%20Gorman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20shock%20of%20the%20rate%20increase%20recently%20has%20put%20a%20damper%20on%20banking%20deals%20%5Band%5D%20capital%20markets%20deals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20FT.%20%26quot%3BThe%20minute%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20has%20concretely%20signaled%20that%20they've%20stopped%20raising%20rates%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20point%20at%20which%20they%20first%20do%20a%20rate%20cut%2C%20these%20markets%20will%20take%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmorgan-stanley-gorman-warren-buffett-regional-banks-svb-risks-crisis-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703243899000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6388e65cb4290800185cc981%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fmorgan-stanley-gorman-warren-buffett-regional-banks-svb-risks-crisis-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22James%20Gorman%20slammed%20bad%20managers%20and%20predicted%20dealmaking%20will%20surge%20once%20it's%20clear%20interest%20rates%20have%20peaked.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40insider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fmorgan-stanley-gorman-warren-buffett-regional-banks-svb-risks-crisis-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Kharge%20Googly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%20meeting%20of%20the%2028-party%20INDIA%20alliance%20did%20not%20produce%20a%20common%20vision%20document%20listing%20an%20agenda%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20in%202024.%20All%20talk%20of%20setting%20up%20a%20campaign%20secretariat%20seemed%20to%20have%20vanished%20into%20thin%20air.%20So%20did%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20convener%2C%20after%20months%20of%20fevered%20speculation%20about%20assigning%20the%20role%20to%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20or%20the%20host%20of%20the%20first%20Patna%20conclave%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20MP%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20(JDU)%2C%20Sunil%20Pintu%2C%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Btea-biscuit%20session%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20the%20samosa%20had%20been%20omitted%20due%20to%20the%20Congress's%20pecuniary%20crunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20faced%20plenty%20of%20darts%20from%20allies%20over%20its%20state%20election%20reverses%20and%20was%20blamed%20for%20its%20refusal%20to%20accommodate%20the%20seat%20requests%20of%20allies%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)'s%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20had%20confabulated%20bilaterally%20before%20the%20meeting%2C%20stumped%20the%20alliance%20collective%2C%20especially%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20by%20pitching%20the%20name%20of%20their%20party's%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20as%20the%20acceptable%20%26quot%3BDalit%20prime%20ministerial%20face%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20and%20AAP%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%20are%20wary%20of%20the%20Congress's%20demand%20for%20seats%20on%20their%20turfs.%20Earlier%2C%20Kejriwal%20had%20announced%20at%20Bathinda%20that%20AAP%20would%20contest%20all%2013%20seats%20in%20Punjab.%20The%20Congress%20had%20won%20nine%20of%20those%20in%20the%202019%20national%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20all%20available%20indications%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20is%20ready%20to%20set%20two%20seats%20aside%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20Bengal%20(Congress%20won%20two%20without%20an%20alliance%20in%202019)%20but%20has%20a%20condition%20-%20the%20Congress%20must%20give%20it%20one%20each%20in%20Assam%20and%20Meghalaya%2C%20both%20states%20where%20the%20Trinamool%20is%20a%20debutant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kharge%20googly%20by%20Mamata-Kejriwal%20thus%20had%20a%20Machiavellian%20undertone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20(CWC)%2C%20which%20met%20on%20December%2021%2C%20sidestepped%20the%20suggestion.%20Kharge%20deflected%20the%20issue%20by%20focussing%20the%20strobe%20light%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20by%20conveying%20the%20party's%20%26quot%3Bfervent%20appeal%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%202.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20yatra%20has%20been%20planned%20in%20January.%20Within%20the%20CWC%2C%20there%20was%20some%20scepticism%20about%20its%20feasibility%20and%20timing.%20It%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20the%20reaction%20of%20INDIA%20alliance%20parties%2C%20who%2C%20by%20and%20large%2C%20seem%20less%20than%20enthused%20by%20Rahul's%20leadership%20abilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENationwide%20seat-sharing%2C%20the%20fulcrum%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20has%20been%20shelved%20till%20mid-January.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20preferred%20the%20year-end.%20The%20last%20conclave%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20August%2031%20and%20September%201%20had%20set%20a%20September-end%20deadline.%20The%20Congress%2C%20hoping%20to%20score%20big%20in%20its%20one-on-one%20battles%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20state%20elections%2C%20had%20postponed%20the%20exercise.%20Despite%20intense%20criticism%20from%20allies%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20laser-focused%20on%20the%20polls.%20Now%20it%20is%20back%20to%20negotiating%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20CWC%20meeting%2C%20the%20December%2019%20conclave%20seemed%20to%20recede%20to%20the%20background%20amid%20blame%20fixing%20over%20the%20party's%20debilitating%20defeat.%20Octogenarian%20Kharge%2C%20who%20has%20weathered%20many%20a%20storm%20in%20his%20distinguished%20five-decade%20career%2C%20was%20quick%20to%20sidestep%20calls%20to%20project%20him%20as%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20INDIA%20meet%2C%20he%20asserted%20that%20he%20had%20never%20projected%20himself%20as%20a%20Dalit%20leader%2C%20and%20that%20talk%20of%20a%20PM%20could%20only%20take%20place%20once%20there%20are%20MPs.%20His%20humility%20notwithstanding%2C%20his%20acceptability%20and%20his%20party's%20position%20as%20Telamon%20of%20the%20alliance%20was%20reflected.%20Axiomatically%2C%20the%20unacceptability%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20alliance%20politics%20was%20underscored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee%20is%20also%20said%20to%20have%20suggested%20that%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20be%20the%20common%20candidate%20against%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20Varanasi%20for%202024.%20Analysts%20in%20Kolkata%20are%20wondering%20why%20%26quot%3BDidi%26quot%3B%20doesn't%20fancy%20herself%20as%20the%20David%20of%20Varanasi%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20needling%20the%20Congress%20and%20rejecting%20the%20CPI%20(M)%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20also%20has%20in%20her%20hands%20the%20undercurrent%20of%20a%20rebellion%20in%20the%20Trinamool%20ranks%2C%20from%20those%20who%20view%20her%20nephew%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20Bengal's%20gen-next.%20Abhishek%20wants%20many%20present%20MPs%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20after%20the%20conclave%2C%20while%20defending%20her%20party%20MP%20Kalyan%20Banerjee's%20act%20of%20mimicking%20Vice%20President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankar%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20targeted%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%20taking%20videos%20on%20his%20mobile%20phone.%20If%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20not%20done%20so%2C%20she%20said%2C%20the%20incident%20would%20not%20have%20blown%20up%20so%20much.%20(but%20despite%20defending%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%2C%20Mamata%20excluded%20him%20from%20the%2010-member%20team%20of%20MPs%20she%20took%20along%20for%20her%20meeting%20with%20Modi%20on%20December%2020)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20fair%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20was%20making%20a%20video%20of%20the%20parody%20on%20his%20cell%20phone%20became%20evident%20only%20when%20TV%20cameras%20showed%20him%20doing%20so.%20The%20chasm%20between%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20largest%20party%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20and%20its%20regional%20partners%20is%20all%20too%20apparent.%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20comments%20betray%20that%20rift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leaders%20questioned%20whether%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20talks%20with%20their%20bete%20noire%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20in%20UP.%20Despite%20Kharge's%20objection%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20harped%20on%20his%20PDA%20(Pichhda-Dalit%20alliance)%20formula%2C%20a%20strategy%20aimed%20against%20the%20BSP.%20Mayawati%20has%20stayed%20away%20from%20the%20INDIA%20talks.%20The%20BSP%20has%20a%20notable%20presence%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20in%20other%20states%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20winning%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20prompted%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20has%20been%20sceptical%20of%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs).%20An%20attempt%20to%20pass%20a%20unanimous%20resolution%20sharing%20this%20scepticism%20did%20not%20take%20off%20on%20December%2019.%20Many%20alliance%20leaders%20felt%20that%20the%20resolution%20should%20be%20limited%20to%20demanding%20that%20the%20VVPAT%20(voter%20verified%20paper%20audit%20trail)%20slip%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20voter%20who%20can%20then%20put%20it%20in%20a%20ballot%20box%20after%20verifying%20their%20vote.%20This%20option%20prevailed%20over%20the%20Congress'%20outright%20rejection%20of%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%2C%20perhaps%20chagrined%20over%20Kharge%20getting%20preference%20over%20him%2C%20is%20said%20to%20have%20lost%20his%20shirt%20when%20DMK%20leaders%20demanded%20an%20English%20translation%20of%20his%20Hindi%20speech.%20Pointing%20out%20that%20Hindi%20is%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20official%20languages%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20went%20on%20to%20endorse%20renaming%20the%20country%20as%20Bharat%2C%20which%20had%20been%20a%20red%20rag%20for%20many%20alliance%20partners%2C%20especially%20the%20Congress%20and%20DMK.%20Many%20Hindi-belt%20leaders%20have%20been%20upset%20with%20the%20DMK's%20abrasive%20stance%20on%20Sanatan%20Dharm.%20The%20North-South%20chasm%20resurfaced%20as%20a%20sore%20during%20the%20alliance%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201989%2C%20Devi%20Lal%20was%20used%20by%20VP%20Singh%20as%20a%20decoy%20to%20thwart%20Chandra%20Shekhar's%20elevation%20as%20Prime%20Minister.%20Chandra%20Shekhar%2C%20having%20agreed%20to%20back%20down%20after%20being%20assured%20that%20Devi%20Lal%20would%20be%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20was%20stunned%20when%20Devi%20Lal%20proposed%20VP%20Singh's%20name%20instead.%20Seasoned%20observers%20wonder%20if%20by%20propping%20up%20Kharge%2C%20Mamta%20Banerjee%20is%20hoping%20for%20an%20opportunity%20in%20case%20the%20BJP%20misses%20the%20halfway-mark%20in%202024.%20Her%20supporters%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20like%20Nitish%20Kumar-backers%20in%20Patna%2C%20have%20been%20rooting%20for%20her%20as%20the%20opposition's%20face.%20Nitish%20Kumar%20could%20be%20the%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20of%202024%2C%20his%20supporters%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20enthusiasm%20and%20bonhomie%20that%20marked%20previous%20INDIA%20meetings%20and%20press%20conferences%20was%20missing%20on%20December%2019.%20As%20has%20been%20seen%20in%20the%20past%20meetings%2C%20many%20leaders%20skipped%20the%20post-meet%20press%20interaction.%20Kejriwal%20had%20abandoned%20the%20briefing%20in%20Patna.%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Lalu%20Yadav%20did%20so%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20left%20in%20a%20huff%20from%20Mumbai.%20In%20all%20instances%2C%20these%20luminaries%20had%20%26quot%3Ba%20flight%20to%20catch%26quot%3B.%20All%20of%20them%20travel%20by%20special%20aircraft%2C%20not%20by%20scheduled%20commercial%20airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2019%2C%20as%20Kharge%20faced%20the%20media%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Lalu%20Yadav%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20were%20not%20by%20his%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20Editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703243760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fi0ds1nik_mamata-banerjee-arvind-kejiwal-pti_625x300_22_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmamata-banerjee-arvind-kejriwals-kharge-googly-4722438%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fourth%20meeting%20of%20the%2028-party%20INDIA%20alliance%20did%20not%20produce%20a%20common%20vision%20document%20listing%20an%20agenda%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20in%202024.%20All%20talk%20of%20setting%20up%20a%20campaign%20secretariat%20seemed%20to%20have%20vanished%20into%20thin%20air.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmamata-banerjee-arvind-kejriwals-kharge-googly-4722438%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmamata-banerjee-arvind-kejriwals-kharge-googly-4722438%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmamata-banerjee-arvind-kejriwals-kharge-googly-4722438%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Colorado%20Supreme%20Court%20Justices%20Receive%20Threats%20Over%20Ruling%20Against%20Trump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Colorado%20Supreme%20Court%20justices%20who%20barred%20Donald%20Trump%20from%20the%20Republican%20primary%20ballot%20in%20the%20state%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20the%2014th%20Amendment%20are%20receiving%20violent%20threats%20on%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Colorado%20court%20ruling%20comes%20through%20the%20US%20Constitution's%20insurrection%20clause%20with%20the%20argument%20being%20that%20he%20was%20in%20office%20and%20broke%20his%20oath%20during%20the%202021%20attack%20on%20the%20Capitol%20after%20Joe%20Biden%20won%20the%20Presidential%20elections.%20The%20insurrection%20clause%20says%20Trump%20can't%20return%20to%20office%20unless%20two-thirds%20of%20Congress%20allows%20him%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20from%20Advance%20Democracy%2C%20a%20non-partisan%20non-profit%20organisation%2C%20revealed%20the%20presence%20of%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20violent%20rhetoric%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20justices%20and%20Democrats%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20according%20to%20CBS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvance%20Democracy%20President%20Daniel%20J.%20Jones%20said%20that%20they%20were%20seeing%20significant%20violent%20language%20and%20threats%20against%20the%20Colorado%20justices%20and%20others%20perceived%20to%20be%20behind%20Tuesday's%20Colorado%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling.%20%26quot%3BThe%20normalisation%20of%20this%20type%20of%20violent%20rhetoric%20is%20cause%20for%20significant%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20most%20alarming%20threats%20were%20found%20on%20fringe%20websites%2C%20with%20one%20post%20calling%20to%20%26quot%3Bbehead%20judges%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bslam%20dunk%20a%20judge's%20baby%20into%20the%20trash%20can.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20social%20media%20users%20have%20gone%20as%20far%20as%20sharing%20personal%20information%20such%20as%20email%20addresses%2C%20phone%20numbers%20and%20office%20building%20addresses%20of%20the%20justices%2C%20further%20escalating%20concerns%20about%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20legal%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJones%2C%20a%20former%20FBI%20investigator%20and%20staffer%20for%20the%20Senate%20Intelligence%20Committee%2C%20told%20NBC%20that%20the%20normalisation%20of%20this%20violent%20rhetoric%20and%20lack%20of%20remedial%20action%20by%20social%20media%20entities%20is%20cause%20for%20significant%20concern.%20Trump's%20statements%20to%20delegitimise%20and%20politicise%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20courts%20serve%20as%20a%20key%20driver%20of%20the%20violent%20rhetoric%2C%20Jones%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPolitical%20leaders%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20political%20aisle%20need%20to%20speak%20out%20against%20these%20calls%20for%20violence%2C%20and%20social%20media%20platforms%20need%20to%20reassess%20their%20role%20in%20hosting%20and%20promoting%20this%20rhetoric%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Colorado%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20a%204-3%20decision%2C%20recognised%20the%20importance%20of%20their%20ruling%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20public%20reaction.%20They%20emphasised%20their%20duty%20to%20apply%20the%20law%20impartially.%20This%20decision%20now%20leads%20to%20a%20legal%20showdown%20in%20the%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20over%20a%20key%20constitutional%20issue%2C%20which%20could%20impact%20Trump's%20eligibility%20for%20the%20presidency%20should%20the%20top%20court%20rule%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703243700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F37qhi8qg_colorado-supreme-court_625x300_22_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcolorado-supreme-court-justices-receive-threats-over-ruling-against-donald-trump-4722365%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Colorado%20Supreme%20Court%20justices%20who%20barred%20Donald%20Trump%20from%20the%20Republican%20primary%20ballot%20in%20the%20state%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20the%2014th%20Amendment%20are%20receiving%20violent%20threats%20on%20social%20media%20platforms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcolorado-supreme-court-justices-receive-threats-over-ruling-against-donald-trump-4722365%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcolorado-supreme-court-justices-receive-threats-over-ruling-against-donald-trump-47