.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F22153213%2FF9vo5rrWsAAbeUY.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20government%E2%80%99s%20amendment%20to%20the%20Assam%20Police%20Act%20in%202022%20has%20%E2%80%9Cseverely%20constrained%E2%80%9D%20enforcing%20accountability%20of%20the%20police%20personnel%20guilty%20of%20serious%20misconduct%2C%20a%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20based%20study%20has%20revealed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20study%2C%20%E2%80%9CPolice%20Complaints%20Authority%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20Status%2C%20Gaps%2C%20Challenges%E2%80%9D%2C%20published%20by%20the%20well-known%20rights%20international%20rights%20body%2C%20the%20Commonwealth%20Human%20Rights%20Initiative%20(CHRI)%2C%20has%20underlined%20that%20though%20Assam%20is%20among%20a%20few%20states%20to%20have%20a%20functional%20State%20Police%20Accountability%20Commission%20(SPAC)%20since%202008%20as%20per%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20directive%2C%20the%20amendment%20made%20to%20the%20state%20Police%20Act%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20in%202022%20has%20severely%20compromised%20the%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20independence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20September%202022%2C%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20demand%20to%20send%20the%20Bill%20to%20a%20select%20committee%20was%20rejected%20by%20the%20speaker%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20walk-out%20by%20the%20opposition%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flegal.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findustry%2Fbill-to-amend-assam-police-act-passed-congress-gogoi-stage-walk-out%2F94314989%5C%22%3Epassing%20of%20the%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20a%20voice%20vote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CHRI%20study%2C%20based%20on%20data%20supplied%20by%20the%20Commission%2C%20has%20shown%20that%20the%20amendment%20had%20weakened%20the%20accountability%20of%20police%20personnel%20by%20%E2%80%9Creducing%20the%20mandate%20of%20SPAC%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20study%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20before%20the%20amendment%2C%20the%20commission%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20empowered%20with%20advisory%20and%20guidance%20providing%20functions%20with%20respect%20to%20misconduct%20as%20well%20and%20it%20served%20as%20an%20important%20check%20against%20biased%20inquiries%20and%20provided%20a%20powerful%20fillip%20to%20police%20accountability.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20with%20the%20state%20legislature%20amending%20the%20Police%20Act%20which%20included%20restructuring%20the%20district-level%20authorities%2C%20it%20has%20become%20difficult%20to%20demand%20accountability%20from%20the%20Assam%20police.%20These%20district-level%20authorities%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20only%20a%20desk%20that%20forwards%20the%20complaints%20received%20further%20up%20than%20initiating%20an%20inquiry%2C%20as%20mandated%20by%20the%20apex%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETill%20the%20state%20Police%20Act%20was%20amended%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Assam%20SPAC%20didn%E2%80%99t%20reject%20complaints%20without%20initiating%20an%20inquiry.%20In%202022%20and%202023%20(till%20March)%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20complaints%20were%20closed%20without%20inquiry%2C%20most%20likely%20due%20to%20SPAC%E2%80%99s%20reduced%20mandate%20following%20the%20legislative%20amendments%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20study%20has%20further%20underlined%20that%20the%20Commission%20no%20longer%20has%20the%20power%20to%20monitor%20the%20pendency%20of%20the%20inquiries%20at%20regular%20intervals.%20Parsing%20the%20data%20provided%20by%20the%20Commission%20through%20RTI%2C%20the%20CHRI%20study%20could%20establish%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20%E2%80%9Clow%20number%20of%20recommendations%20for%20departmental%20inquiries%20and%20no%20recommendations%20for%20registration%20of%20FIRs%E2%80%9D%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20act%20of%20reducing%20the%20SPAC%E2%80%99s%20mandate%20without%20a%20complementary%20increase%20in%20that%20of%20the%20(district%20accountability%20authorities%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20cause%20of%20concern%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20underlined.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20comes%20across%20as%20significant%20in%20the%20study%20is%20that%20the%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20in%20its%20annual%20reports%20have%20been%20ignored%20by%20the%20state%20government.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20its%202018-2022%20annual%20report%2C%20SPAC%20recommended%20that%20the%20state%20government%20allot%20land%20to%20it%20for%20a%20permanent%20office%20building%20so%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20huge%20sum%20of%20money%E2%80%9D%20being%20spent%20towards%20renting%20office%20space%20could%20be%20saved%20by%20the%20state%20exchequer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20noteworthy%20suggestion%20was%20demanding%20accountability%20from%20the%20state%20director%20general%20of%20police%2C%20binding%20an%20obligation%20on%20him%20to%20ensure%20quarterly%20status%20reports%20to%20SPAC%20on%20departmental%20enquiries%20against%20police%20officers.%20Also%20that%20the%20investigation%20of%20an%20FIR%20against%20a%20police%20officer%20should%20be%20conducted%20by%20an%20officer%20senior%20by%20at%20least%20one%20rank%20to%20him%2Fher%20or%20by%20the%20state%20CID.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20no%20action%20stated%20for%20the%20DGP%20if%20he%20falters%20in%20conducting%20inquiries%2C%20the%20accountability%20of%20that%20public%20office%20has%20been%20reduced%20substantially.%20The%20CHRI%20report%20recommends%20that%20to%20make%20SPAC%20act%20as%20per%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20mandate%2C%20%E2%80%9Cunreasonable%20delay%20or%20failure%E2%80%9D%20on%20his%20part%20to%20report%20to%20Assam%20SPAC%20about%20action%20taken%20on%20its%20recommendations%20be%20considered%20%E2%80%9Cmisconduct%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Model%20Police%20Bill%2C%202015%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20Commission%20is%20headed%20by%20retired%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20Justice%20B.P.%20Katakey%20as%20its%20chairperson%20with%20former%20state%20DGP%20Mukesh%20Sahay%2C%20retired%20IAS%20officer%20Gaurav%20Bohra%20and%20retired%20state%20service%20officer%20Moniratna%20Mahanta%20as%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20has%20highlighted%20that%20their%20tenure%20would%20be%20over%20by%20this%20December%2C%20and%20the%20state%20government%20must%20ensure%20that%20those%20posts%20are%20filled%20in%20time.%20Currently%2C%20though%20the%20SC%20directive%20has%20sought%20one%20of%20its%20members%20to%20be%20a%20woman%20and%20one%20a%20member%20of%20the%20civil%20society%2C%20the%20Assam%20SPAC%20has%20not%20adhered%20to%20it.%20It%20has%20also%20underlined%20that%20the%20Commission%20is%20constituted%20without%20any%20transparency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20Sarma%20government%20came%20to%20power%2C%20Assam%20has%20been%20in%20the%20news%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Fassam-under-the-scanner-after-rise-in-cases-of-encounter-deaths-since-2017%2Farticle66790106.ece%5C%22%3Esharp%20increase%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%E2%80%98encounter%20deaths%E2%80%99%20by%20state%20police%2C%20leading%20some%20civil%20society%20groups%20to%20seek%20the%20Gauhati%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20to%20inquire%20into%20it.%20Chief%20minister%20Sarma%20was%20seen%20in%20public%20in%202021%20directing%20state%20police%20to%20shoot%20suspected%20criminals%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20legs%E2%80%9D%20if%20they%20try%20to%20flee%20from%20custody.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703242841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F22153213%2FF9vo5rrWsAAbeUY.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fassam-amendment-police-act-constrains-serious-misconduct%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20study%20by%20the%20Commonwealth%20Human%20Rights%20Initiative%20has%20underlined%20that%20though%20Assam%20is%20among%20a%20few%20states%20to%20have%20a%20functional%20State%20Police%20Accountability%20Commission%2C%20the%20amendments%20to%20the%20Act%20severely%20compromised%20its%20independence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fassam-amendment-police-act-constrains-serious-misconduct%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netizens%20call%20Fighter%20song%20'mediocre'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703242838000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106212363%2Cimgsize-26332.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnetizens-think-ishq-jaisa-kuch-song-from-fighter-is-just-mediocre-but-love-hrithik-roshan-and-deepika-padukone-say-death-by-chocolate%2Farticleshow%2F106212167.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106212167.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EHrithik%20Roshan%20and%20Deepika%20Padukone%20steal%20the%20show%20in%20their%20new%20song%20from%20'Fighter'%2C%20however%2C%20people%20are%20disappointed%20by%20Vishal-Sheykhar's%20composition%20and%20some%20also%20feel%20Hrithik%20looks%20better%20with%20Katrina%20Kaif...%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnetizens-think-ishq-jaisa-kuch-song-from-fighter-is-just-mediocre-but-love-hrithik-roshan-and-deepika-padukone-say-death-by-chocolate%2Farticleshow%2F106212167.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%2