0country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20noted%20in%20its%20December%2013%20verdict%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20business%20of%20EC%20staff%20cannot%20result%20in%20citizens%20going%20unrepresented.%20That%20is%20unthinkable%20and%20would%20amount%20to%20sabotaging%20the%20entire%20constitutional%20framework%20which%2C%20we%20trust%2C%20is%20what%20even%20the%20EC%20did%20not%20want.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20had%20said%20it%20is%20busy%20with%20%E2%80%9Cother%20elections%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%201951%2C%20has%20it%20that%20a%20vacancy%20in%20the%20parliament%20has%20to%20be%20filled%20in%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20heard%20in%20January%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.economictimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fec-moves-sc-against-hc-order-calling-for-early-bypolls-in-pune%2Famp_articleshow%2F106191936.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEconomic%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20paper%20has%20noted%20that%20the%20case%20will%20have%20multiple%20implications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fate%20constituencies%20of%20Ambala%2C%20Ghazipur%20and%20Chandrapur%20which%20became%20vacant%20between%20March%20to%20May%2C%20and%20should%20have%20gone%20to%20the%20polls%20in%20September-October%2C%20could%20also%20be%20decided.%20However%2C%20elected%20MPs%20would%20only%20have%20a%20two-%20to%20three-month-long%20term%20considering%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20is%20scheduled%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703241918000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F22171517%2Fvoter-id.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fec-challenges-bombay-hc-order-to-hold-pune-by-polls-petitioner-files-caveat-in-sc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20had%20said%20it%20could%20not%20hold%20by-elections%20in%20the%20Pune%20seat%20which%20has%20been%20vacant%20since%20late%20March%20as%20it%20is%20busy%20with%20%26quot%3Bother%20elections%20in%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fec-challenges-bombay-hc-order-to-hold-pune-by-polls-petitioner-files-caveat-in-sc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Biden%20Administration's%20Delay%20of%20Gun%20Shipments%20to%20Israel%20Police%20Is%20Simply%20Too%20Little%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F22175839%2FUntitled-design-9.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20morning%20in%202016%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20economist%20who%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20leaders%20of%20his%20agricultural%20village%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20saw%20that%20there%20were%20clashes%20between%20children%20and%20Israeli%20soldiers.%20The%20small%20children%20threw%20stones%20at%20the%20soldiers%20who%20entered%20the%20village%20playground%20and%20he%20knew%20that%20the%20incident%20could%20end%20in%20their%20arrest%20or%20injury.%20He%20advanced%20to%20the%20scene%20with%20his%20hands%20raised%20in%20the%20air%2C%20yelling%20at%20the%20children%20to%20stop%20and%20go%20home.%20The%20children%20left%20and%20then%20he%20tried%20to%20leave%20as%20well%2C%20when%20one%20of%20the%20soldiers%20shot%20a%20rubber%20bullet%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20his%20forehead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20scar%20remained%2C%20but%20he%20recovered%20from%20the%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20in%20his%20village%2C%20he%20was%20repeatedly%20arrested%20and%20attacked%20by%20both%20soldiers%20and%20settlers%2C%20but%20he%20felt%20a%20responsibility%20and%20whenever%20there%20was%20an%20incident%20in%20the%20village%2C%20he%20would%20go%20there.%20When%20there%20was%20