s.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-red-sea-taskforce-gets-limited-backing-from-some-allies%2Farticleshow%2F106210639.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-red-sea-taskforce-gets-limited-backing-from-some-allies%2Famp_articleshow%2F106210639.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-red-sea-taskforce-gets-limited-backing-from-some-allies%2Famp_articleshow%2F106210639.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Protest%20at%20the%20Parliament%20Should%20Be%20Seen%20as%20Fearlessness%2C%20Not%20Terror%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20never%20fails%20to%20amuse%20me%20is%20the%20unbearable%20pomposity%2C%20the%20self-absorption%2C%20and%20the%20conceit%20of%20our%20representatives%20in%20the%20parliament.%20Two%20young%20people%20protested%2C%20in%20an%20admittedly%20unusual%20manner%2C%20by%20releasing%20plumes%20of%20yellow%20smoke%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Two%20more%20were%20part%20of%20this%20audacious%20plan.%20They%20believe%20that%20politics%20is%20the%20art%20of%20the%20impossible.%20And%20they%20showed%20us%20how.%20But%20%E2%80%98august%E2%80%99%20members%20of%20the%20parliament%2C%20scuttling%20here%20and%20there%20to%20escape%20%E2%80%98poisonous%20gas%E2%80%99%2C%20have%20typed%20the%20intrusion%20as%20nothing%20less%20than%20an%20attack%20on%20national%20security.%20Seriously%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20that%20four%20young%20people%20were%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20to%20make%20us%20hear%2C%20in%20a%20rather%20dramatic%20fashion%20%3Cem%3Ea%20la%3C%2Fem%3E%20Bhagat%20Singh%2C%20was%20their%20voice%20of%20pain%2C%20despair%2C%20and%20frustration.%20They%20made%20an%20unexpected%20entry%20into%20the%20House%2C%20simply%20because%20they%20wanted%20their%20representatives%20and%20their%20country%20to%20heed%20their%20justifiable%20protest%20at%20unemployment%2C%20deprivation%2C%20and%20despondency.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20else%20could%20they%20have%20done%3F%20Their%20voices%20are%20just%20not%20heard%20by%20those%20who%20strut%20the%20corridors%20of%20power.%20Demonstrations%20are%20frowned%20upon%2C%20dissent%20suppressed%2C%20and%20alternative%20visions%20of%20politics%20dismissed%20as%20the%20work%20of%20anti-nationals.%20When%20people%20do%20not%20have%20access%20to%20any%20channel%20to%20express%20grievances%2C%20politics%20takes%20to%20the%20streets%2C%20or%20in%20this%20case%2C%20right%20into%20parliament.%20This%20is%20the%20lesson%20of%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpangs-of-unemployment-why-indias-youth-is-turning-to-bhagat-singh%5C%22%3EPangs%20of%20Unemployment%3A%20Why%20India%E2%80%99s%20Youth%20is%20Turning%20to%20Bhagat%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConsider%20the%20background%3B%20abject%20poverty.%20The%20prime%20minister%20has%20announced%20the%20extension%20of%20free%20rations%20to%2081%20crore%20Indians.%20The%20implication%20is%20that%20millions%20of%20our%20fellow%20citizen%20go%20to%20bed%20hungry.%20Not%20a%20pretty%20picture%20for%20a%20country%20that%20is%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%98atma%20nirbhar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(self%20sufficient)%2C%20least%20of%20all%20one%20that%20is%20located%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98amrit%20kaal%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20government%20is%20not%20statistic%20friendly.%20So%20we%20do%20not%20know%20how%20many%20people%20fall%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%2C%20or%20even%20what%20the%20poverty%20line%20is.%20But%20if%2081%20crore%20people%20cannot%20buy%20food%20for%20themselves%2C%20the%20deprivation%20they%20are%20mired%20in%20defies%20imagination.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20this%20tragic%20fact%20of%20our%20national%20life%20that%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20policy%20makers%20by%20our%20young%20intruders.%20The%20response%20was%20to%20slap%20the%20UAPA%20upon%20them.%20Consider%20the%20irony.%20The%20majesty%20of%20the%20house%20was%20not%20harmed%20when%20one%20MP%20heaped%20communal%20slurs%20upon%20a%20fellow%20parliamentarian.%20Basic%20notions%20of%20justice%2C%20civility%2C%20and%20gender%20sensitivity%20were%20grossly%20violated%20when%20a%20woman%20MP%20raised%20questions%20related%20to%20national%20wellbeing%20and%20the%20handing%20over%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20resources%20to%20one%20capitalist.%20She%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20House.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20when%20two%20young%20people%20reenacting%20the%20actions%20of%20their%20hero%20Bhagat%20Singh%20descend%20into%20the%20House%20and%20raise%20uncomfortable%20questions%2C%20the%20majesty%20of%20the%20house%20is%20dented.%20Perhaps%20they%20were%20reclaiming%20%E2%80%98the%20people%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20House%20that%20has%20been%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20with%20deleterious%20consequences.%20The%20phrase%20%E2%80%98We%20the%20People%E2%80%99%20is%20empty%20until%20and%20unless%20the%20people%20bring%20the%20malaise%20of%20the%20country%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20ruling%20authorities%20through%20unusual%20actions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20did%20so%20by%20picking%20up%20a%20handful%20of%20salt%20and%20breaking%20the%20law.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20notion%20of%20the%20people%20presents%20itself%20to%20us%20in%20tangible%20forms%20through%20such%20actions%20performed%20with%20a%20degree%20of%20unmatched%20fearlessness.%20We%20would%20do%20well%20to%20recollect%20that%20Gandhi%20had%20written%20that%20%E2%80%9CI%20hope%20also%20to%20achieve%20the%20end%20by%20demonstrating%20that%20real%20%3Cem%3Eswaraj%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20come%20not%20by%20the%20acquisition%20of%20authority%20by%20a%20few%20but%20by%20the%20acquisition%20of%20the%20capacity%20by%20all%20to%20resist%20authority%20when%20it%20is%20abused.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20swaraj%20is%20to%20be%20attained%20by%20educating%20the%20masses%20to%20a%20sense%20of%20their%20capacity%20to%20regulate%20and%20control%20authority%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748-300x210.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748-1024x715.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-638156%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22838%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20precisely%20this%20aspect%20of%20politics%2C%20of%20educating%20the%20people%20into%20a%20sense%20of%20their%20own%20capacity%20to%20regulate%20and%20control%20authority%2C%20that%20is%20repressed%20by%20authoritarian%20governments.%20They%20dream%20of%20a%20society%20where%20no%20one%20dare%20speak%20or%20act%20against%20the%20supreme%20leader%2C%20only%20acclaim%20him.%20Hannah%20Arendt%20in%20her%20famous%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Human%20Condition%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20(1958)%2C%C2%A0%20had%20written%20that%20exasperation%20with%20the%20three%20fold%20frustration%20of%20action%3A%20the%20unpredictability%20of%20its%20outcome%2C%20the%20irreversibility%20of%20the%20process%2C%20and%20the%20anonymity%20of%20its%20authors%2C%20leads%20to%20the%20denouncement%20of%20action%20and%20speech%20in%20particular%2C%20and%20politics%20in%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20always%20been%20a%20great%20temptation%2C%20for%20men%20of%20action%20no%20less%20than%20for%20men%20of%20thought%2C%20to%20find%20a%20substitute%20for%20action%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20the%20realm%20of%20human%20affairs%20may%20escape%20the%20haphazardness%20and%20moral%20irresponsibility%20inherent%20in%20a%20plurality%20of%20agents.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20as%20old%20as%20recorded%20history.%20Generally%20speaking%2C%20such%20men%20seek%20shelter%20from%20popular%20politics%2C%20that%20can%20go%20this%20way%20or%20that%2C%20by%20dreaming%20of%20a%20society%20where%20one%20man%2C%20isolated%20from%20all%20others%2C%20remains%20master%20of%20his%20doings%20from%20beginning%20to%20end.%20This%20attempt%20to%20replace%20acting%20with%20making%20is%20manifest%20in%20the%20whole%20body%20of%20argument%20against%20%E2%80%98democracy%E2%80%99%2C%20which%2C%20the%20more%20consistently%20and%20better%20reasoned%20it%20is%2C%20will%20turn%20into%20an%20argument%20against%20the%20essentials%20of%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArendt%20was%20prescient%2C%20and%20this%20is%20an%20understatement.%20The%20politics%20of%20impossibility%20represented%20as%20thought%20and%20action%20in%20the%20public%20realm%20is%20plural%20and%20contested.%20What%20is%20not%20contested%2C%20is%20not%20politics.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20acceptable%20to%20our%20rulers.%20They%20attempt%20to%20do%20away%20with%20politics%20by%20doing%20away%20with%20the%20public%20sphere.%20And%20%E2%80%98we%20the%20people%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20have%20sadly%20helped%20them%20by%20constituting%20ourselves%20as%20subjects%20of%20a%20ruler%2C%20not%20as%20citizens%20of%20a%20democracy%20that%20have%20the%20right%20to%20call%20the%20government%20to%20account.%20We%20are%20told%20to%20attend%20to%20our%20personal%20affairs%20and%20perform%20duties.%20The%20business%20of%20politics%20is%20best%20left%20to%20power.%20And%20we%20do%20so.%20I%20am%20afraid%20that%20we%20as%20the%20people%20have%20played%20the%20game%20of%20the%20holders%20of%20power.%20We%20have%20retreated%20from%20the%20public%20sphere%20into%20the%20private%2C%20armed%20with%20the%20blissful%20conviction%20that%20a%20group%20of%20men%20can%20take%20care%20of%20us%2C%20and%20of%20politics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20lost%20our%20memory%20of%20resistance%20and%20struggle.%20The%20reduction%20of%20Gandhi%20to%20a%20pair%20of%20spectacles%20has%20proved%20disastrous.%20His%20politics%20has%20been%20reduced%20from%20the%20subversive%20to%20the%20routine%3B%20picking%20up%20the%20broom%20and%20cleaning%20the%20streets.%20Gandhi%2C%20it%20is%20true%2C%20cleaned%20toilets%20at%20the%20meetings%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress.%20But%20he%20did%20much%20more.%20As%20a%20man%20of%20the%20moment%2C%20he%20was%20skilled%20in%20the%20art%20of%20crafting%20political%20strategy.%20He%20showed%20us%20how%20to%20be%20courageous%20and%20fearless.%20%E2%80%98I%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9Chave%20been%20collecting%20descriptions%20of%20s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewaraj%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20One%20of%20these%20is%20the%20abandonment%20of%20the%20fear%20of%20death.%20%E2%80%9CA%20nation%20which%20allows%20itself%20to%20be%20influenced%20by%20the%20fear%20of%20death%20cannot%20attain%20swaraj%2C%20and%20cannot%20retain%20it%20if%20somehow%20obtained.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20do%20we%20not%20see%20these%20young%20intruders%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20fearless%3F%20They%20knew%20the%20consequences%20of%20their%20action.%20Think%20of%20their%20profound%20disappointment%20when%20they%20realised%20that%20the%20people%20they%20had%20elected%20to%20parliament%2C%20who%20luxuriate%20in%20the%20power%20that%20the%20status%20bestows%20upon%20them%2C%20were%20supremely%20indifferent%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20their%20own%20people.%20They%20might%20well%20have%20said-we%20asked%20for%20jobs%2C%20we%20got%20temples%20instead.%20They%20reacted%20in%20the%20only%20way%20they%20could%20%E2%80%93%20with%20courage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fneera-chandhoke%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ENeera%20Chandhoke%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%20was%20a%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20at%20Delhi%20University.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703239501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fprotest-at-the-parliament-should-be-seen-as-fearlessness-not-terror%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Think%20of%20the%20youth's%20profound%20disappointment%20when%20they%20realised%20that%20the%20people%20they%20had%20elected%20to%20parliament%20were%20supremely%20indifferent%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20their%20own%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fprotest-at-the-parliament-should-be-seen-as-fearlessness-not-terror%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CISF%20Asked%20to%20Take%20Over%20Parliament%20Security%20After%20Breach%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26191526%2F1280px-View_of_Lok_Sabha_chamber_in_the_New_Parliament_building_New_Delhi.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20home%20ministry%20has%20asked%20the%20Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force%20(CISF)%20to%20conduct%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20parliament%20to%20establish%20%E2%80%9Cregular%20deployment%20on%20a%20comprehensive%20pattern%E2%80%9D%2C%20days%20after%20a%20security%20breach%20occurred%20on%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmha-parliament-cisf-security-breach-9077141%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20CISF%20will%20collaborate%20with%20Parliament%20Security%20Services%20to%20regulate%20access%20to%20both%20the%20old%20and%20new%20parliament%20complex.%20Currently%2C%20visitor%20frisking%20is%20managed%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2013%2C%20two%20individuals%20with%20smoke%20cans%20jumped%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpangs-of-unemployment-why-indias-youth-is-turning-to-bhagat-singh%5C%22%3Estage%20a%20protest%20against%20rising%20unemployment%2C%20inflation%20and%20poverty%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20were%20accompanied%20by%20two%20others%20who%20remained%20outside%20and%20yelled%20slogans%20like%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Ctanshahi%20nahi%20chalegi%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eand%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Cbharat%20mata%20ki%20jai%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20breach%20prompted%20a%20preliminary%20probe%20by%20a%20committee%2C%20headed%20by%20CRPF%20Director%20General%20Anish%20Dayal%20Singh%2C%20which%20identified%20security%20lapses%20during%20visitor%20frisking.%20Subsequently%2C%20eight%20security%20personnel%20were%20suspended%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmha-parliament-cisf-security-breach-9077141%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20internal%20communication%2C%20MHA%20Under%20Secretary%20Ashutosh%20Kumar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmha-parliament-cisf-security-breach-9077141%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn-principle%20approval%20of%20the%20competent%20authority%20is%20conveyed%20for%20carrying%20out%20the%20survey%20of%20the%20Parliament%20premises%20and%20its%20building%20for%20regular%20deployment%20of%20CISF%20%E2%80%93%20both%20security%20wing%20and%20fire%20wing%20%E2%80%93%20on%20comprehensive%20pattern%20under%20Government%20Building%20Security%20(GBS).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CISF%20has%20initiated%20a%20joint%20survey%20by%20its%20Government%20Building%20Security%20unit%20and%20fire%20wing%20to%20ascertain%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20personnel%20needed%20and%20define%20the%20role%20of%20each%20security%20agency%20involved%20in%20Parliament%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20letter%20from%20a%20DIG-rank%20officer%20outlined%20the%20constitution%20of%20a%20joint%20survey%20board%2C%20with%20Ajay%20Kumar%2C%20DIG%2C%20CISF%20Unit%20CGBS%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20as%20the%20presiding%20officer.%20The%20board%20is%20tasked%20with%20conducting%20the%20survey%20in%20association%20with%20representatives%20of%20the%20parliament%20secretariat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpangs-of-unemployment-why-indias-youth-is-turning-to-bhagat-singh%5C%22%3EPangs%20Of%20Unemployment%3A%20Why%20India%E2%80%99s%20Youth%20Is%20Turning%20To%20Bhagat%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20board%20is%20directed%20to%20submit%20completed%20reports%20for%20Security%20and%20Fire%20Wing%2C%20including%20information%20proforma%20and%20IFD%20chart%20with%20specific%20justifications%20for%20each%20duty%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20pursuance%20of%20MHA%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98in-principle%E2%80%99%20approval%2C%20board%20for%20conducting%20joint%20survey%20of%20Parliament%20premises%20and%20its%20buildings%20for%20regular%20deployment%20of%20CISF%20Security%20and%20Fire%20Wing%20on%20comprehensive%20pattern%2C%20as%20per%20PSU%20and%20fire%20norms%2C%20is%20hereby%20constituted%20with%20Ajay%20Kumar%2C%20DIG%2C%20CISF%20Unit%20CGBS%2C%20New%20Delhi%20as%20presiding%20officer.%20It%20is%20requested%20to%20detail%20other%20members%20of%20the%20joint%20survey%20board%20including%20an%20officer%20with%20technical%20expertise.%20An%20officer%20of%20CISF%20Fire%20Wing%20may%20also%20be%20detailed%20in%20consultation%20with%20the%20Fire%20Directorate.%20The%20survey%20board%20may%20be%20directed%20to%20conduct%20the%20survey%20(as%20per)%20instructions%2F%20guidelines%20issued%20from%20time%20to%20time%20on%20conducting%20surveys%20in%20association%20with%20representative(s)%20of%20the%20Parliament%20Secretariat%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmha-parliament-cisf-security-breach-9077141%2F%5C%22%3Eletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuly%20completed%20survey%20reports%20for%20Security%20and%20Fire%20Wing%20with%20these%20documents%20may%20kindly%20be%20submitted%20to%20this%20Directorate%20at%20the%20earliest%20for%20further%20process%20please%3B%20information%20proforma%2C%20and%20IFD%20chart%20with%20specific%20justification%20for%20each%20duty%20post%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703239236000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26191526%2F1280px-View_of_Lok_Sabha_chamber_in_the_New_Parliament_building_New_Delhi.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcisf-asked-to-take-over-parliament-security-after-breach%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CISF%20will%20collaborate%20with%20Parliament%20Security%20Services%20to%20regulate%20access%20to%20both%20the%20old%20and%20new%20parliament%20complex.%20Currently%2C%20visitor%20frisking%20is%20managed%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20personnel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcisf-asked-to-take-over-parliament-security-after-breach%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Imran%20Khan's%20family%20members%20to%20not%20contest%20upcoming%20elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703238989000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106210350%2Cimgsize-19224.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fimran-khans-family-members-to-not-contest-upcoming-general-elections%2Farticleshow%2F106210294.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106210294.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EImran%20Khan's%20wife%2C%20sisters%2C%20and%20Bushra%20Bibi%20will%20not%20contest%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections%20in%20Pakistan.%20Aleema%20Khan%2C%20Imran%20Khan's%20sister%2C%20made%20this%20statement%20outside%20the%20Islamabad%20High%20Court.%20She%20criticized%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20and%20accused%20him%20of%20not%20allowing%20players%20to%20enter%20the%20political%20field.%20Aleema%20also%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20trial%20in%20the%20cypher%20case%20and%20expressed%20hope%20for%20justice%20from%20Allah%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20Islamabad%20High%20Court%20dismissed%20Imran%20Khan's%20plea%20to%20suspend%20the%20trial%20court's%20verdict%20in%20the%20Toshakhana%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fimran-khans-family-members-to-not-contest-upcoming-general-elections%2Farticleshow%2F106210294.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fimran-khans-family-members-to-not-contest-upcoming-general-elections%2Famp_articleshow%2F106210294.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fimran-khans-family-members-to-not-contest-upcoming-general-elections%2Famp_articleshow%2F106210294.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Star%20Turns%20From%20Prabhas%2C%20Prithviraj%20Are%20Salaar's%20Main%20Draws%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20mind-numbing%20power%20of%20unrelenting%20violence%20is%20on%20full%20display%20over%20all%20of%20three%20hours%20in%20the%20unabashedly%20gory%20%3Ci%3ESalaar%3A%20Part%201%20-%20Ceasefire%3C%2Fi%3E.All%20the%20blood-letting%20that%20the%20film%20revels%20in%20has%20a%20somniferous%20effect%20on%20the%20audience%2C%20lulling%20it%20into%20a%20desensitised%20state%20that%20serves%20to%20make%20the%20shocks%20somewhat%20palatable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Telugu-language%20epic%20-%20this%20critic%20watched%20the%20film's%20Hindi%20dub%20-%20is%20set%20in%20a%20terrain%20that%20is%20far%20less%20dusty%20than%20the%20one%20in%20the%20two%20chapters%20of%20writer-director%20Prashanth%20Neel's%20Kannada%20actioner%20KGF%20was%2C%20the%20heat%20that%20it%20generates%20is%20just%20as%20scalding%20and%20the%20decibel%20levels%20it%20rises%20to%20are%20nearly%20as%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAadhya%20(Shruti%20Haasan)%2C%20who%20returns%20from%20the%20United%20States%20to%20a%20chaotic%20universe%20where%20some%20people%20want%20her%20dead%20because%20of%20an%20act%20that%20her%20father%20committed%20years%20ago%2C%20is%20the%20human%20receptacle%20into%20which%20the%20story%20flows.%20The%20nature%20of%20the%20narration%20that%20she%20receives%20from%20the%20man%20deployed%20to%20keep%20her%20safe%20boggles%20her%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20heard%20the%20convoluted%20saga%20of%20Khansaar%2C%20a%20dreaded%20and%20lawless%20country%20divided%20into%20over%20100%20territories%20and%20populated%20by%20three%20tribes%2C%20to%20its%20bitter%20end%2C%20she%20quips%3A%20Wait%2C%20wait%2C%20I%20need%20a%20drink.%20Daaru%20hai%20kya%3F%20Well%2C%20that%20is%20exactly%20what%20the%20response%20of%20most%20of%20us%20would%20be%20unless%20we%20have%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20keep%20abreast%20of%20director%20Prashanth%20Neel's%20breathless%20storytelling%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20thrives%20on%20piling%20words%20upon%20words%2C%20sounds%20upon%20sounds%2C%20and%20images%20upon%20images%20without%20creating%20space%20for%20the%20slightest%20crevice%20for%20light%20to%20seep%20into.%20The%20film%20-%20it%20rattles%20along%20like%20a%20runaway%20train%20-%20does%20not%20give%20the%20audience%20any%20time%20to%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20is%20not%20necessarily%20meant%20as%20derision.%20There%20is%20something%20about%20the%20hurtling%2C%20bewildering%20rhythm%20of%20Salaar%3A%20Part%201%20that%20ensures%20that%20the%20audience%20is%20never%20let%20off%20the%20hook.%20Such%20is%20the%20pace%20at%20which%20the%20film%20dishes%20out%20the%20details%20of%20its%20plot%20and%20sub-plots%2C%20keeping%20up%20with%20it%20takes%20some%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20not%20allowing%20the%20viewer%20to%20pause%20to%20wonder%20what%20is%20going%20on%2C%20the%20film%20manages%20to%20pass%20off%20its%20dizzying%20momentum%20not%20only%20as%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20its%20design%20but%20also%20as%20its%20primary%20selling%20point.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20maximalist%20pulp%20that%20it%20foists%20upon%20us%2C%20we%20actually%20push%20our%20cognitive%20and%20auditory%20faculties%20as%20far%20as%20we%20can%20to%20grasp%20the%20goings-on%20with%20varying%20degrees%20of%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20half%20of%20Salaar%3A%20Part%201%20is%20devoted%20entirely%20to%20the%20story%20of%20the%20burly%20brooding%20and%20invincible%20Devaratha%20(Prabhas)%2C%20his%20relationship%20with%20his%20mother%20(Easwari%20Rao)%20and%20his%20friendship%20with%20his%20pal%20from%2025%20years%20ago%2C%20Varadha%20Raja%20Mannar%20(Prithviraj%20Sukumaran)%2C%20son%20of%20the%20second%20wife%20of%20the%20ruler%20of%20present-day%20Khansaar%2C%20Raja%20Mannar%20(Jagapathi%20Babu).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20about%2090%20minutes%2C%20the%20film%20sets%20the%20stage%20for%20Deva's%20dramatic%20appearance%20in%20Khansaar%2C%20a%201000-year-old%20principality%20where%20a%20bloody%20battle%20of%20succession%20is%20on%20between%20the%20ruling%20Mannar%20tribe%20and%20the%20Shouraangya%20and%20Ghaniyaar%20tribes%20for%20the%20throne%20occupied%20by%20Varadha's%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaradha%20and%20Deva%20haven't%20seen%20each%20other%20for%20years%20but%20as%20matters%20go%20out%20of%20hand%20in%20Khansaar%20and%20dangers%20of%20a%20palace%20coup%20loom%20over%20the%20rulers%2C%20the%20former%20requests%20the%20latter%20for%20help%2C%20aware%20of%20how%20formidable%20his%20long-separated%20friend%20is%20as%20a%20fearsome%20fighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaradha's%20enemies%20have%20enlisted%20the%20support%20of%20militias%20from%20across%20the%20world%20-%20Russia%2C%20Austria%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20Serbia%20-%20but%20Deva%20is%20a%20veritable%20one-man%20army.%20He%20is%2C%20expectedly%2C%20more%20than%20a%20handful%20for%20any%20outfit%20or%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20crucial%20scene%20in%20the%20first%20half%2C%20the%20reluctant%20Deva%20swings%20into%20action%20to%20save%20Aradhya%20from%20a%20band%20of%20vicious%20goons%20after%20his%20mother%20exhorts%20him%20to%20break%20his%20vow%20of%20non-violence.%20It%20is%20at%20her%20bidding%20that%20he%20had%20decided%20never%20to%20fight%20ever%20again.%20Once%20the%20sluice%20gates%20are%20thrown%20open%2C%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20stop%20Deva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20berserk%20every%20time%20his%20childhood%20pal%20Varadha%20faces%20any%20danger.%20He%20turns%20especially%20fierce%20when%20a%20girl%20is%20in%20distress.%20One%20character%20points%20out%20that%20in%20every%20damsel%20who%20faces%20a%20threat%20from%20men%2C%20he%20sees%20his%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20it%20machine%20guns%2C%20machetes%20or%20just%20his%20bare%20hands%2C%20he%20is%20head%20and%20shoulders%20above%20any%20enemy%20who%20gets%20in%20his%20way.%20He%20bulldozes%20into%20situations%20in%20which%20a%20lot%20of%20blood%20is%20spilled%20amid%20impalements%2C%20dismemberments%20and%20decapitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20a%20pretty%20sight%2C%20but%20the%20heightened%20performative%20quality%20that%20the%20choreography%20imparts%20to%20the%20action%20-%20Deva's%20gaze%20and%20gait%20are%20that%20of%20a%20cocky%20prize%20boxer%20who%20walks%20into%20the%20ring%20knowing%20full%20well%20that%20he%20is%20destined%20to%20win%20-%20delivers%20a%20string%20of%20unsettlingly%20gory%20but%20strangely%20mesmerizing%20moments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FHihakYi5M2I%3Fsi%3DJPYLPY3rlZOefGKC%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visual%20palette%20of%20the%20film%20is%20composed%20of%20muted%20hues%20rather%20than%20full%20splashes%20of%20stark%20colour.%20Salaar%3A%20part%201%20is%20set%20in%20what%20looks%20and%20feels%20like%20an%20exceedingly%20dim%20universe%20where%20the%20stray%20rays%20of%20light%20that%20are%20visible%20are%20never%20of%20the%20uninterrupted%20and%20illuminating%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20subdued%20visuals%2C%20halfway%20through%20the%20second%20half%2C%20are%20punctuated%20with%20the%20dull%20russet%20of%20the%20saris%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20brightly%20designed%20umbrellas%20and%20a%20multi-coloured%20kite%20and%20then%2C%20in%20the%20climactic%20passages%2C%20broken%20by%20the%20sight%20of%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECinematographer%20Bhuvan%20Gowda's%20camerawork%20and%20lighting%20(aided%2C%20of%20course%2C%20by%20the%20hyper-kinetic%20visual%20effects%20and%20the%20elaborate%20digital%20intermediate%20work)%20produce%20frames%20that%20are%20dominated%20by%20fading%20browns%2C%20grimy%20blacks%20and%20gloomy%20greys%20-%20not%20all%20that%20different%20from%20how%20the%20images%20were%20in%20KGF%20-%20to%20create%20a%20grim%20portrait.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sound%20design%20and%20the%20background%20score%2C%20which%20are%20as%20intrusive%20as%20it%20was%20in%20KGF%2C%20bolsters%20the%20feral%20nature%20of%20life%20in%20Khansaar%2C%20a%20place%20where%20the%20ruler%20thrives%20on%20instilling%20fear%20in%20his%20subjects%20and%20his%20foes.%20He%20says%20at%20one%20point%3A%20We%20are%20all%20violent%20men%3B%20violence%20is%20in%20our%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20is%20that%20all.%20One%20of%20Varadha's%20main%20adversaries%20drugs%20100%20men%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%20and%20turns%20them%20into%20bloodthirsty%20hounds%20who%20pounce%20like%20hyenas%20on%20anything%20that%20is%20red.%20One%20of%20the%20two%20protagonists%20warns%20that%20Khansaar%20will%20soon%20turn%20red%20either%20because%20of%20leaping%20flames%20or%20flowing%20blood.%20The%20film%20delivers%20generous%20doses%20of%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolid%20star%20turns%20from%20Prabhas%20and%20Prithviraj%20Sukumaran%20are%20the%20main%20draws%20of%20Salar%3A%20Part%201%20-%20Ceasefire.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20film's%20appeal%20lies%20in%20the%20lure%20of%20unbridled%20excess.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703238900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F9go4sjeg_salaar_625x300_22_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsalaar-part-1-ceasefire-review-star-turns-from-prabhas-prithviraj-sukumaran-are-the-main-draws-2-5-stars-4722179%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Salaar%3A%20Part%201-%20Ceasefire%20Review%3A%20Such%20is%20the%20pace%20at%20which%20the%20film%20dishes%20out%20the%20details%20of%20its%20plot%20and%20sub-plots%2C%20keeping%20up%20with%20it%20takes%20some%20doing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsalaar-part-1-ceasefire-review-star-turns-from-prabhas-prithviraj-sukumaran-are-the-main-draws-2-5-stars-4722179%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jungkook's%20%E2%80%983D%E2%80%