uch%20the%20ground%20again%2C%20so%20also%2C%20different%20systemic%20arrangements%20of%20history%20have%20a%20life%2C%20move%20on%2C%20and%20return%20when%20we%20think%20what%20is%20gone%20never%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20consider%20this%3A%20the%20advent%20of%20inductive%20science%20brought%20with%20it%20a%20flush%20of%20enquiry%20and%20possibility%20in%20a%20slew%20of%20human%20thought%20and%20material%20endeavour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20wake%2C%20science%20opened%20up%20a%20market%20of%20both%20ideas%20and%20goods%20and%20services%20for%20capital%20to%20operate%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECapitalism%20in%20its%20burgeoning%20required%20the%20destruction%20of%20old%20feudal%20constraints%20across%20the%20board%2C%20and%20so%20spawned%20the%20idea%20of%20democracy%20as%20an%20idea%2C%20rooted%20in%20the%20productive%20potential%20and%20dignity%20of%20the%20human%20individual.%20But%20when%20it%20came%20into%20full%20ascendance%2C%20Capital%20saw%20that%20science%2C%20which%20had%20brought%20it%20into%20being%20was%20now%20its%20enemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20it%20required%20was%20technology%2C%20not%20science%2C%20or%20if%20you%20like%2C%20a%20science%20that%20was%20now%20directing%20all%20its%20ingenuity%20not%20to%20explore%20further%20truths%2C%20or%20question%20Capitalism%20and%20the%20social%20order%20it%20came%20to%20spawn%2C%20but%20to%20devise%20newer%20instruments%20for%20generating%20and%20accumulating%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20this%20endeavour%20began%20to%20see%20that%20along%20with%20science%2C%20democracy%20too%20was%20a%20potential%20antagonist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20wealth%20came%20to%20be%20monopolised%2C%20ideas%20of%20social%2C%20economic%20and%20political%20equity%20spelt%20danger%20to%20the%20now%20entrenched%20power%20of%20Capital%20across%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClever%20protagonists%20soon%20saw%20that%20the%20protection%20and%20furtherance%20of%20what%20they%20had%20achieved%20would%20now%20require%20strategies%20for%20quelling%20the%20free%20mental%20agency%20of%20people%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20could%20achieve%20this%20project%20of%20silencing%20better%20than%20the%20deployment%20of%20race%2C%20religion%20and%20nationalism%2C%20ruthlessly%20propagated%20among%20the%20mass%20of%20people%20through%20facilitations%20made%20available%20by%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitler%20used%20the%20radio%20to%20great%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20the%20relentless%20use%20of%20electronic%20media%2C%20and%20now%20what%20is%20called%20rather%20outlandishly%20the%20%E2%80%98social%20media%E2%80%99%20to%20condition%20the%20%E2%80%98popular%20mind%E2%80%99%20to%20unquestioningly%20receive%20whatever%20the%20posers-that-be%20dish%20out%20in%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20interest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cartwheel%2C%20however%2C%20turned%20after%20the%20defeat%20of%20Fascism%20in%20Europe%2C%20and%20a%20renewed%20liberalism%20seemed%20to%20once%20again%20suffuse%20the%20political%20climate%20of%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20destruction%20wrought%20by%20war%20facilitated%20the%20ingress%20of%20the%20benevolent%20Marshall%20plan%20to%20rebuild%20Europe%20as%20a%20democratic%20enclave%20and%2C%20more%20to%20the%20point%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20market%E2%80%9D%20ready%20to%20receive%20the%20munificence%20of%20American%20productive%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDecolonisation%20across%20continents%20released%20a%20flush%20of%20human%20freedom%20and%20new%20dreams%20among%20the%20oppressed%20peoples%20of%20erstwhile%20slave%20states%2C%20as%20it%20were%2C%20to%20make%20their%20own%20new%20future%20along%20the%20best%20principles%20of%20political%20and%20economic%20liberalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocracy%20once%20again%20became%20a%20desired%20handmaiden%2C%20and%20new%2C%20emancipatory%20constitutions%20came%20to%20be%20fashioned%20in%20so%20many%20decolonised%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C