.in%2Frights%2Fcost-of-suspending-members-of-parliament%5C%22%3E15%20crore%20electors%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20(and%20more%2C%2018%20crore%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha)%20whom%20the%20suspended%20146%20members%20of%20the%20Indian%20parliament%20represent%2C%20are%20equal%20citizens%20of%20the%20republic%20who%20have%20charged%20their%20now-suspended%20representatives%20with%20the%20task%20of%20holding%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%20to%20account%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way%2C%20and%20those%20others%20who%20think%20that%20the%20only%20legitimate%20citizens%20and%20electors%20are%20those%20who%20have%20voted%20for%20the%20ruling%20party%20five%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20those%20of%20us%20who%20still%20believe%20that%20parliamentary%20etiquette%2C%20an%20idea%20now%20routinely%20thrown%20at%20helplessly%20protesting%20public%20representatives%2C%20requires%20most%20of%20all%20that%20when%20parliament%20is%20in%20session%2C%20the%20executive%20must%20first%20make%20averments%20in%20the%20House%20on%20issues%20of%20national%20concern%20before%20they%20proceed%20to%20propagandise%20among%20the%20captive%20media%2C%20and%20there%20are%20those%20who%20think%20parliamentary%20etiquette%20is%20limited%20just%20to%20how%20members%20should%20sit%20or%20stand%20in%20the%20House%2C%20or%20what%20papers%20or%20placards%20they%20carry%20even%20if%20out%20of%20desperation%20at%20never%20being%20allowed%20to%20open%20their%20mouth%20on%20issues%20that%20most%20need%20to%20be%20aired%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpeople%E2%80%99s%20interest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20those%20of%20us%20who%20begin%20to%20see%20that%20the%20right%20wing%20ultimately%2C%20desires%20a%20one-party%20parliament%2C%20and%20those%20who%20think%20why%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwhy%20not%E2%80%9D%20Indians%20are%20also%20those%20who%20never%20cease%20to%20berate%20the%20communist%20parties%20for%20desiring%20one-party%20rule.%20Never%20mind