nced-to-life-in-hospital-4722023%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbritish-teen-hacker-behind-gta-6-leaks-sentenced-to-life-in-hospital-4722023%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20Returns%20Home%20From%20South%20Africa%2C%20Another%20Batter%20Ruled%20Out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20team%20superstar%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reportedly%20returned%20home%20due%20to%20a%20family%20emergency%2C%20just%20days%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20South%20Africa.%20The%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20sources%2C%20however%2C%20have%20confirmed%20that%20the%20iconic%20batter%20will%20be%20back%20in%20time%20for%20the%20first%20Test%2C%20which%20begins%20on%20December%2026%2C%20against%20the%20Proteas%20in%20Centurion.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20BCCI%20had%20released%20wicket-keeper%20batter%20Ishan%20Kishan%20from%20the%20squad%20for%20the%20Test%20series%20over%20a%20personal%20matter.%20KS%20Bharat%20was%20named%20as%20his%20replacement%20for%20the%202-match%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20been%20learned%20that%20India's%20opening%20batter%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20has%20been%20ruled%20out%20of%20the%20two-Test%20series%20because%20of%20a%20fracture%20in%20his%20finger.%20%26quot%3BRuturaj%20Gaikwad%20has%20been%20ruled%20out%20of%20the%20two-Test%20series%20with%20ring%20finger%20fracture%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaikwad%20had%20sustained%20the%20injury%20on%20his%20finger%20while%20trying%20to%20take%20a%20catch%20during%20the%20second%20ODI%20against%20South%20Africa%20earlier%20this%20week.%20The%20BCCI%20hasn't%20yet%20named%20a%20replacement%20for%20the%20young%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Test%20series%20is%20set%20to%20mark%20the%20return%20of%20Kohli%2C%20along%20with%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20pacer%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20a%20few%20other%20members%20of%20India's%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20squad.%20Since%20India's%20heartbreaking%20defeat%20against%20Australia%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%2C%20Kohli%2C%20Rohit%20and%20some%20other%20senior%20members%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%20have%20been%20away%20from%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20had%20missed%20India's%20T20I%20series%20against%20South%20Africa%20as%20well%20as%20the%20white-ball%20assignments%20against%20South%20Africa.%20However%2C%20he%20made%20himself%20available%20for%20the%20Test%20series%20from%20the%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20yet%20known%20what%20the%20'family%20emergency'%20is%20that%20prompted%20Virat%20to%20return%20home%20just%204%20days%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Test%20series.%20But%2C%20the%20emergency%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20a%20complicated%20one%20as%20Kohli%20has%20assured%20the%20BCCI%20of%20his%20return%20to%20the%20team%20before%20the%20Test%20series%20begins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20squad%20for%20Tests%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERohit%20Sharma%20(C)%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Shreyas%20Iyer%2C%20KL%20Rahul%20(wk)%2C%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20Shardul%20Thakur%2C%20Mohd.%20Siraj%2C%20Mukesh%20Kumar%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20(VC)%2C%20Prasidh%20Krishna%2C%20KS%20Bharat%20(wk)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703237040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F6idin1so_kohli-pc_625x300_22_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fvirat-kohli-returns-home-from-south-africa-due-to-family-emergency-report-4721752%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20returned%20home%20from%20South%20Africa%20on%20Friday%20morning%2C%20sources%20have%20confirmed%20NDTV.%20But%2C%20the%20batter%20will%20head%20back%