%20the%20Hindutva%20outfit%20has%20issued%20a%20clarification%20of%20sorts%2C%20stating%20that%20%E2%80%9CSangh%20is%20not%20against%20caste%20census%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERSS%20publicity%20in-charge%20Anand%20Ambedkar%20clarified%20on%20December%2021%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CSangh%20is%20not%20against%20caste%20census%2C%20but%20such%20an%20exercise%20should%20be%20used%20to%20achieve%20overall%20development%20of%20society%20while%20ensuring%20that%20no%20harm%20is%20caused%20to%20social%20harmony%20and%20unity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20ago%2C%20Sridhar%20Gadge%2C%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20Vidarbha%20chief%2C%20while%20speaking%20to%20legislators%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20had%20outrightly%20rejected%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20claiming%20it%20would%20divide%20society%20and%20harm%20%E2%80%9Cnationalism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20see%20any%20benefits%20in%20it%20(caste%20census)%2C%20instead%20only%20harm.%20It%20is%20the%20root%20of%20inequality%20and%20we%20have%20a%20clear%20stand%20that%20there%20should%20be%20no%20inequality%2C%20enmity%20or%20quarrel%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gadge%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGadge%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20on%20caste%20census%20came%20in%20tandem%20with%20P%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmodi-rss-against-caste-census-demand%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520organisation%2527s%2520Vidharbha%2520chief%2520Sridhar%2Cwould%2520only%2520deepen%2520the%2520rift%25E2%2580%259D.%5C%22%3Erime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20rejection%20of%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20his%20parliamentary%20constituency%20Varanasi.%20On%20December%2018%2C%20addressing%20a%20rally%2C%20Modi%20attacked%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20batting%20for%20caste%20census%20by%20stating%20that%20he%20knew%20only%20four%20castes%20%E2%80%93%20youth%2C%20women%2C%20deprived%20sections%20and%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20stand%20is%2C%20however%2C%20not%20in%20line%20with%20BJP%20leader%20and%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fcaste-census-shah-says-bjp-never-opposed-it-needs-careful-thought-9012522%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DUnion%2520Home%2520Minister%2520Amit%2520Shah%2Cat%2520an%2520%25E2%2580%259Cappropriate%2520time%25E2%2580%259D.%5C%22%3Ewho%20had%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20assembly%20elections%20that%20the%20party%20has%20%E2%80%9Cnever%20opposed%20the%20idea%20of%20caste%20census%E2%80%9D.%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20statement%20was%20to%20counter%20the%20opposition%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20promise%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20caste%20census%20if%20it%20returns%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20was%20seen%20making%20a%20U-turn%20on%20caste-based%20reservations.%20While%20he%20was%20seen%20endorsing%20it%2C%20his%20statement%20in%202015%2C%20however%2C%20was%20not%20in%20its%20support.%20That%202015%20opposition%20of%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20against%20caste-based%20reservation%20is%20widely%20seen%20by%20political%20observers%20to%20have%20harmed%20BJP%20in%20the%20Bihar%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20publicity%20chief%20Manmohan%20Vaidya%20had%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Frss-chief-mohan-bhagwat-reservation-caste-udhayanidhi-stalin-bjp%23read-more%5C%22%3Eopposed%20caste-based%20reservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20Jaipur%20Literature%20Festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20contradictory%20statements%20by%20the%20BJP%20top%20leaders%20and%20those%20from%20its%20ideological%20fount%20on%20caste%20census%20come%20across%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20keep%20the%20issue%20ambivalent%20in%20the%20public%20sphere%2C%20keeping%20in%20mind%20not%20just%20the%20recent%20assembly%20polls%20where%20the%20Congress%20had%20categorically%20supported%20caste%20census%20but%20al